   277	        and any external callers continue to work without invasive
   278	        refactoring. New gateway code uses :meth:`reserve_slot` directly so
   279	        the cap-exceed branch is reachable in the WS handler. Unit tests stay
   280	        well under ``max_sessions`` so this alias's cap enforcement does not

