    34	_PERSONA_ID_RE: Final[re.Pattern[str]] = re.compile(r"\A[a-z][a-z0-9_-]{0,63}\Z")
    35	"""Allowed shape for a ``persona_id`` token passed on the CLI.
    36	
    37	Tokens are joined with ``personas_dir`` to build a file path, so anything
    38	containing ``..`` / ``/`` / null bytes / leading dots would allow reading
    39	files outside the personas directory. This regex (lowercase alnum plus
    40	``_`` and ``-``, leading letter, ≤64 chars) matches the existing persona
    41	YAML filenames (``kant.yaml``, ``nietzsche.yaml``, ``rikyu.yaml``) and
    42	forbids the rest.
