    | 105 +++++++++-\nsrc/erre_sandbox/cli/eval_run_golden.py            |  14 ++\nsrc/erre_sandbox/integration/gateway.py            | 193 +++++++++++++++-\nsrc/erre_sandbox/integration/protocol.py           |  43 +++++\nsrc/erre_sandbox/world/tick.py                     |  10 ++\ntests/test_codex_hooks/__init__.py                 |   0\ntests/test_codex_hooks/test_shell_bypass_policy.py | 189 ++++++++++++++\ntests/test_integration/test_gateway.py             | 144 ++++++++++-\ntests/test_world/test_runtime_lifecycle.py         | 135 ++++++++++\n```\n\n## Implementation summary\n\n### SH-2 (commit `e31562e`) — WS 3-layer auth (token + Origin + cap)\n\n- `integration/protocol.py:62`+ — `DEFAULT_ALLOWED_ORIGINS: Final[tuple[str, ...]] = ()` (empty = check disabled, Godot empty-Origin compat) + `MAX_ACTIVE_SESSIONS: Final[int] = 8` + `SessionCapExceededError(current, cap)`\n- `integration/gateway.py` — new `WSAuthConfig` frozen dataclass (4 fields, all default-disabled). `Registry.__init__` accepts `max_sessions`; `reserve_slot` raises `SessionCapExceededError` atomically inside the event loop; `add()` kept as deprecated alias delegating to `reserve_slot` (cap-safe under tests since they stay below 8). `ws_observe` pre-accept gates: Origin allow-list (close 1008), shared-token via `secrets.compare_digest` (close 1008), session-cap pre-check (close 1013, fast path). Race-safe `reserve_slot` in ACTIVE phase: if a slot was filled between the pre-check and reserve, send in-band `session_cap_exceeded` ErrorMsg + close 1013.\n- `bootstrap.py` — 4 BootConfig fields. `_resolve_ws_token`: explicit → env `ERRE_WS_TOKEN` → file `var/secrets/ws_token` → None. `_validate_ws_auth_config`: raises `RuntimeError` at startup when `host==\"0.0.0.0\"` AND no Origin allowlist AND not (`require_token=True` AND token present). Operator escape hatches printed in the message: `--allowed-origins`, `--require-token + var/secrets/ws_token`, or `--host=127.0.0.1`.\n- `__main__.py` — 4 argparse flags `--ws-token / --require-token / --allowed-origins / --max-sessions`. comma-list parsing for origins.\n- `tests/test_integration/test_gateway.py::TestWebSocketAuth` — 6 cases (back-compat default / token missing 1008 / token mismatch 1008 / token match continues / origin reject 1008 / cap exceeded 1013).\n- Docs: `architecture.md:328` auth posture updated; `development-guidelines.md` token rotation runbook; `README.md` `var/secrets/` provisioning + opt-in flag examples.\n\n### SH-1 (commit `b3bba97`) — Codex hook + CI shell-bypass guard\n\n- `.codex/hooks.json:30` — matcher widens to `apply_patch|Edit|Write|exec_command|Bash`.\n- `.codex/hooks/pre_tool_use_policy.py` — `shell_write_targets(command)` helper (7 regex patterns: sed -i / perl -pi / tee / cat>>HEREDOC / generic > / python -c open() / Path().write_text). `main()` pre-check: if shell command contains any `src/erre_sandbox/...` write target, return `deny(...)` immediately. `deny()` itself unchanged (Codex protocol JSON `permissionDecision=\"deny\"` in stdout, exit 0 — see SH-FOLLOWUP-1 in this task's `decisions.md`).\n- `.github/workflows/ci.yml` — new `policy-grep-gate` job (`fetch-depth: 0`, 5-min timeout). 3 steps: (a) banned-import grep for openai|anthropic|bpy; (b) `uv run ruff check --select T201 src/erre_sandbox` so the pyproject T201 exemption + per-line noqa are honoured naturally — see SH-FOLLOWUP-2 — preserving the existing `inference/ollama_adapter.py:145` CI-green baseline; (c) `.steering/[YYYYMMDD]-*/` completeness check (skipped when no `src/erre_sandbox/**/*.py` diff).\n- `tests/test_codex_hooks/test_shell_bypass_policy.py` — 5 red-team subprocess cases (sed-in-place / echo>> / tee / python-c open() / cat heredoc) + 2 negative paths (grep / write to /tmp). Each asserts JSON `hookSpecificOutput.permissionDecision == \"deny\"`.\n\n### Codex 13th MEDIUM (commit `69f3b48`)\n\n- `world/tick.py:814` — `logger.warning(\"runtime backlog overflow: drops=%d maxsize=%d\", ...)` added inside the overflow branch so out-of-band SRE log fires alongside the in-band ErrorMsg.\n- `cli/eval_run_golden.py:_resolve_memory_db_path` — TOCTOU disclosure docstring added (no test; race window is theoretical given single-user /tmp + same-UID var/eval).\n- `tests/test_world/test_runtime_lifecycle.py` — 7 new cases on `TestWorldRuntimeEnvelopeQueue`: maxsize-1 / maxsize / maxsize+1 boundary, monotonic overflow count across two bursts, `_consume_result` path also drops oldest (helper-shared), `logger.warning` emission via caplog, `recv_envelope` cancel cleanliness.\n\n## Fact-check sheet (run on this branch)\n\n```\n$ git rev-parse --abbrev-ref HEAD\nfeature/security-hardening-pre-m10-followup\n\n$ git log --oneline main..HEAD\n69f3b48 feat(observability+tests): SH-5 logger.warning + SH-4/SH-5 coverage\nb3bba97 feat(codex): hook + CI shell-bypass guard (SH-1)\ne31562e feat(ws): shared-token + Origin + session cap (SH-2)\n\n$ git diff main..HEAD -- data/eval/golden src/erre_sandbox/evidence\n<empty>\n\n$ git diff main..HEAD -- src/erre_sandbox/schemas.py\n<empty>\n\n$ grep -n '^SCHEMA_VERSION' src/erre_sandbox/schemas.py\n44:SCHEMA_VERSION: Final[str] = \"0.10.0-m7h\"\n\n$ uv run ruff check src tests\nAll checks passed!\n\n$ uv run ruff format --check src tests\n218 files already formatted\n\n$ uv run mypy src\nSuccess: no issues found in 82 source files\n\n$ uv run pytest -q -m \"not godot and not eval and not spike and not training and not inference\"\n1399 passed, 32 skipped, 54 deselected, 3 warnings in 4.71s\n```\n\nTest delta from PR #170 baseline (1378): +21 cases = 6 TestWebSocketAuth + 5 SH-1 red-team + 2 SH-1 negative + 1 MEDIUM observability caplog + 6 MEDIUM boundary/monotonic/_consume_result/cancel + 1 SH-2 back-compat default.\n\n## Required review output format\n\nReturn ONE document with sections:\n\n1. **Executive verdict** — one of: `ADOPT` / `ADOPT-WITH-CHANGES` / `BLOCK`. Quote 1–2 sentences.\n2. **HIGH findings** (each numbered HIGH-N): file + line, severity rationale, recommended fix. HIGH ⇒ must be fixed before merge. Be specific — Claude will reflect each one in a follow-up commit.\n3. **MEDIUM findings** (MEDIUM-N): may be deferred via `decisions.md` ADR addendum, but state your recommendation.\n4. **LOW findings** (LOW-N): optional / nit / blockers.md candidates.\n5. **META** — anything systemic about the implementation approach, the SH-FOLLOWUP-1/SH-FOLLOWUP-2 judgement calls, or the scope of the M10-0 gate. In particular, evaluate:\n   - **META-1**: does this 3-commit set close the M10-0 go/no-go gate that META-1 of your 13th review (PR #170) flagged? If not, what is still missing?\n   - **META-2**: did the SH-FOLLOWUP-1 decision (keep `deny()` returning exit 0 + JSON, do not migrate to exit 2) regress any property of the Codex hook protocol you can verify against the upstream Codex docs?\n   - **META-3**: SH-FOLLOWUP-2 routed the SH-1 print backstop through `ruff check --select T201` instead of a literal grep. Confirm whether the `inference/ollama_adapter.py:145` raw `print()` is actually a legitimate gap (and thus the ruff-equivalent design is fine) or a real existing-violation we should burn down here.\n6. **Fact-check sheet** — restate any of the commands in the sheet above whose output you re-ran or any new ones you ran independently. Quote the actual output.\n\n## Scope-specific risks for you to evaluate\n\n- **SH-2 startup gate**: is the `RuntimeError` on `host=0.0.0.0 + all gates off` going to break the user's existing daily LAN workflow in a way the runbook (`docs/development-guidelines.md`) does not adequately surface? Note: memory `feedback_crlf_canonical_for_md5.md` and the SH-2 ADR explicitly preserve `host=0.0.0.0` default; the gate's contract is \"you must opt into ONE protection\".\n- **SH-2 reserve_slot atomicity**: `len(self._queues) >= self._max_sessions` followed by `self._queues[session_id] = queue` is atomic relative to other event-loop callers because Python's asyncio is single-threaded, but verify the pre-accept fast-path and the in-loop authoritative `reserve_slot` are wired correctly so the race window (between pre-check and reserve) is closed by `_send_error` + close 1013, not by a silent allow.\n- **SH-1 shell regex coverage**: the 7 regex patterns in `shell_write_targets` aim for the 5 red-team cases plus generic `>`/`>>` redirects with file extensions. Identify obvious bypasses I missed (e.g., `python -c \"exec(...)\"` indirection, base64-encoded payloads, `xargs` chains).\n- **SH-1 CI gate behaviour on PRs from forks**: `policy-grep-gate` uses `fetch-depth: 0` and `git diff origin/main...HEAD`. Does this work for fork PRs where `origin` resolves to the fork? Check the GitHub Actions behaviour.\n- **MEDIUM logger.warning** placement: I added the log inside the existing `if self._envelopes.maxsize > 0 and self._envelopes.full()` branch, after the count was bumped but before the warning ErrorMsg was enqueued. Confirm there is no path where the count is bumped but the log is skipped, or vice versa.\n- **MEDIUM test coverage**: `test_consume_result_path_uses_drop_oldest_helper` calls the private `_enqueue_with_drop_oldest` directly rather than constructing a `CycleResult` and driving `_consume_result`. Is the shared-helper proof sufficient, or do you want a higher-fidelity test that exercises the full envelope loop?\n\n## Constraints (must be preserved)\n\n- `data/eval/golden/` / `src/erre_sandbox/evidence/` unchanged (verified empty in fact-check sheet)\n- `SCHEMA_VERSION = \"0.10.0-m7h\"` unchanged (verified)\n- No new `ControlEnvelope` types; the gateway uses existing `ErrorMsg.code` with new string value `\"session_cap_exceeded\"` (lifecycle scope) — consistent with SH-5's `\"runtime_backlog_overflow\"`\n- `require_token=False` default (back-compat)\n- `host=0.0.0.0` default preserved\n- `idea_judgement*.md` / `data/eval/golden/_checksums_mac_received.txt` deliberately excluded from these commits\n\n## Self-tests to run if you have shell\n\n```bash\nuv run ruff check src tests\nuv run ruff format --check src tests\nuv run mypy src\nuv run pytest -q -m \"not godot and not eval and not spike and not training and not inference\"\nuv run pytest tests/test_integration/test_gateway.py tests/test_codex_hooks tests/test_world/test_runtime_lifecycle.py -q\n\n# Codex hook smoke (SH-FOLLOWUP-1 JSON match form)\necho '{\"tool\":\"exec_command\",\"tool_input\":{\"command\":\"sed -i s/x/y/ src/erre_sandbox/x.py\"}}' \\\n  | uv run python .codex/hooks/pre_tool_use_policy.py \\\n  | jq -e '.hookSpecificOutput.permissionDecision == \"deny\"'\n```\n\nReturn your review as plain text starting with the executive verdict. Brevity is welcome; depth is welcome too — pick what serves the gate decision.\n","images":[],"local_images":[],"text_elements":[]}}
.steering/20260515-security-hardening-pre-m10-followup/codex-review.stderr:6148:/Users/johnd/.codex/sessions/2026/05/15/rollout-2026-05-15T18-02-57-019e2adf-e667-7241-b4b7-edcb4561a395.jsonl:66:{"timestamp":"2026-05-15T09:04:00.367Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"function_call_output","call_id":"call_Av8Gmzyf2oUCw2b8K9GLEpou","output":"Chunk ID: 76c229\nWall time: 0.0000 seconds\nProcess exited with code 0\nOriginal token count: 2429\nOutput:\n     1\t#!/usr/bin/env python3\n     2\tfrom __future__ import annotations\n     3\t\n     4\timport re\n     5\tfrom pathlib import Path\n     6\tfrom typing import Any\n     7\t\n     8\tfrom _erre_common import emit_json, latest_task, read_payload, relative_path, repo_root, task_status\n     9\t\n    10\tIMPL_PREFIX = \"src/erre_sandbox/\"\n    11\t\n    12\t# SH-1 — shell-write detection. These regex patterns flag the canonical\n    13\t# ways a shell command can write to a file on disk so the hook can reject\n    14\t# any write that targets ``src/erre_sandbox/``. The matcher in\n    15\t# ``.codex/hooks.json`` widens to ``exec_command|Bash`` so this path now\n    16\t# fires for tool calls that previously bypassed the ``apply_patch|Edit|\n    17\t# Write`` filter. False negatives are acceptable since the CI\n    18\t# ``policy-grep-gate`` job is a second backstop; false positives only\n    19\t# fire on shell commands that target ``src/erre_sandbox/`` so the user\n    20\t# can re-issue via Edit/Write.\n    21\tSHELL_WRITE_PATTERNS: list[re.Pattern[str]] = [\n    22\t    # sed -i / gsed -i [-i.bak] [-e ...] PATH (in-place edit)\n    23\t    re.compile(\n    24\t        r\"\\b(?:g?sed)\\s+-i(?:\\s+(?:''|\\.\\w+))?\"\n    25\t        r\"(?:[^|;]*?\\s+-e\\s+(?:'[^']*'|\\\"[^\\\"]*\\\"|\\S+))?\"\n    26\t        r\"[^|;]*?\\s(?P<path>[\\w./-]+\\.\\w+)\\b\",\n    27\t    ),\n    28\t    # perl -pi / -pie -e ... PATH\n    29\t    re.compile(\n    30\t        r\"\\bperl\\s+-pi(?:e)?(?:[^|;]*?\\s+-e\\s+(?:'[^']*'|\\\"[^\\\"]*\\\"))?\"\n    31\t        r\"[^|;]*?\\s(?P<path>[\\w./-]+\\.\\w+)\\b\",\n    32\t    ),\n    33\t    # tee [-a] PATH (write or append)\n    34\t    re.compile(r\"\\btee\\b(?:\\s+-a)?\\s+(?P<path>[\\w./-]+\\.\\w+)\\b\"),\n    35\t    # cat > PATH << EOF (heredoc redirect)\n    36\t    re.compile(r\"\\bcat\\s+>>?\\s*(?P<path>[\\w./-]+\\.\\w+)\\s*<<\"),\n    37\t    # Generic shell redirect ``> PATH.ext`` or ``>> PATH.ext`` — catches\n    38\t    # echo / printf / dd / generic pipelines. The ``\\.\\w+`` tail keeps\n    39\t    # this from matching ``> /dev/null`` and the like.\n    40\t    re.compile(r\"(?<![<>])>>?\\s*(?P<path>[\\w./-]+\\.\\w+)\\b\"),\n    41\t    # python -c \"...open('PATH', 'w'|'a'|'wb'|'ab'...).write(...)...\"\n    42\t    re.compile(\n    43\t        r\"python3?\\s+-c\\s+['\\\"][^'\\\"]*?open\\s*\\(\\s*\"\n    44\t        r\"['\\\"](?P<path>[^'\\\"]+)['\\\"]\\s*,\\s*['\\\"][wa]b?\\+?\",\n    45\t    ),\n    46\t    # python -c \"...Path('PATH').write_(text|bytes)...\"\n    47\t    re.compile(\n    48\t        r\"python3?\\s+-c\\s+['\\\"][^'\\\"]*?Path\\s*\\(\\s*\"\n    49\t        r\"['\\\"](?P<path>[^'\\\"]+)['\\\"]\\s*\\)\\s*\\.\\s*write_(?:text|bytes)\",\n    50\t    ),\n    51\t]\n    52\t\n    53\t\n    54\tdef shell_write_targets(command: str) -> list[str]:\n    55\t    \"\"\"Return paths a shell command would write to (best-effort regex).\n    56\t\n    57\t    The hook treats any returned path that lies under ``IMPL_PREFIX`` as\n    58\t    a violation (see :func:`main`). Returning a path outside ``IMPL_PREFIX``\n    59\t    is harmless because :func:`is_impl_path` filters it out at the call\n    60\t    site; the caller never reads content from this helper, only the path\n    61\t    list.\n    62\t    \"\"\"\n    63\t    targets: list[str] = []\n    64\t    seen: set[str] = set()\n    65\t    for pattern in SHELL_WRITE_PATTERNS:\n    66\t        for match in pattern.finditer(command):\n    67\t            path = match.group(\"path\")\n    68\t            if path and path not in seen:\n    69\t                seen.add(path)\n    70\t                targets.append(path)\n    71\t    return targets\n    72\t\n    73\t\n    74\tBANNED_PATTERNS: list[tuple[str, re.Pattern[str]]] = [\n    75\t    (\n    76\t        \"cloud LLM API imports are forbidden in src/erre_sandbox\",\n    77\t        re.compile(r\"^\\s*(?:import\\s+(?:openai|anthropic)\\b|from\\s+(?:openai|anthropic)\\b)\"),\n    78\t    ),\n    79\t    (\n    80\t        \"bpy imports are forbidden in src/erre_sandbox because Blender/GPL code is isolated\",\n    81\t        re.compile(r\"^\\s*(?:import\\s+bpy\\b|from\\s+bpy\\b)\"),\n    82\t    ),\n    83\t    (\n    84\t        \"print() is forbidden in src/erre_sandbox; use logging instead\",\n    85\t        re.compile(r\"^\\s*print\\s*\\(\"),\n    86\t    ),\n    87\t]\n    88\t\n    89\t\n    90\tdef deny(reason: str) -> int:\n    91\t    emit_json(\n    92\t        {\n    93\t            \"hookSpecificOutput\": {\n    94\t                \"hookEventName\": \"PreToolUse\",\n    95\t                \"permissionDecision\": \"deny\",\n    96\t                \"permissionDecisionReason\": reason,\n    97\t            }\n    98\t        }\n    99\t    )\n   100\t    return 0\n   101\t\n   102\t\n   103\tdef patch_targets(command: str) -> dict[str, list[str]]:\n   104\t    targets: dict[str, list[str]] = {}\n   105\t    current: str | None = None\n   106\t    for line in command.splitlines():\n   107\t        for marker in (\"*** Add File: \", \"*** Update File: \", \"*** Delete File: \"):\n   108\t            if line.startswith(marker):\n   109\t                current = line[len(marker) :].strip()\n   110\t                targets.setdefault(current, [])\n   111\t                break\n   112\t        else:\n   113\t            if current and line.startswith(\"+\") and not line.startswith(\"+++\"):\n   114\t                targets[current].append(line[1:])\n   115\t    return targets\n   116\t\n   117\t\n   118\tdef direct_targets(tool_input: dict[str, Any]) -> dict[str, list[str]]:\n   119\t    result: dict[str, list[str]] = {}\n   120\t    for key in (\"file_path\", \"path\"):\n   121\t        value = tool_input.get(key)\n   122\t        if isinstance(value, str) and value:\n   123\t            content = tool_input.get(\"new_string\") or tool_input.get(\"content\") or \"\"\n   124\t            if isinstance(content, str):\n   125\t                result[value] = content.splitlines()\n   126\t    edits = tool_input.get(\"edits\")\n   127\t    target = tool_input.get(\"file_path\") or tool_input.get(\"path\")\n   128\t    if isinstance(edits, list) and isinstance(target, str):\n   129\t        lines: list[str] = []\n   130\t        for edit in edits:\n   131\t            if isinstance(edit, dict) and isinstance(edit.get(\"new_string\"), str):\n   132\t                lines.extend(edit[\"new_string\"].splitlines())\n   133\t        result[target] = lines\n   134\t    return result\n   135\t\n   136\t\n   137\tdef target_map(payload: dict[str, Any]) -> dict[str, list[str]]:\n   138\t    tool_input = payload.get(\"tool_input\")\n   139\t    if not isinstance(tool_input, dict):\n   140\t        return {}\n   141\t    command = tool_input.get(\"command\")\n   142\t    if isinstance(command, str) and \"*** Begin Patch\" in command:\n   143\t        return patch_targets(command)\n   144\t    return direct_targets(tool_input)\n   145\t\n   146\t\n   147\tdef is_impl_path(path: str) -> bool:\n   148\t    return path.startswith(IMPL_PREFIX)\n   149\t\n   150\t\n   151\tdef check_banned(path: str, lines: list[str]) -> str | None:\n   152\t    if not path.endswith(\".py\") or not is_impl_path(path):\n   153\t        return None\n   154\t    for line in lines:\n   155\t        for label, pattern in BANNED_PATTERNS:\n   156\t            if pattern.search(line):\n   157\t                return f\"{label}: {path}: {line.strip()}\"\n   158\t    return None\n   159\t\n   160\t\n   161\tdef main() -> int:\n   162\t    payload = read_payload()\n   163\t    root = repo_root(payload)\n   164\t    # SH-1: shell-write bypass guard. The PreToolUse matcher in\n   165\t    # ``.codex/hooks.json`` widens to ``exec_command|Bash`` so this branch\n   166\t    # is now reachable for shell tool calls. Any shell command that writes\n   167\t    # into ``src/erre_sandbox/`` is rejected regardless of the would-be\n   168\t    # content — the change must go through Edit/Write/apply_patch so the\n   169\t    # same policy guards (banned imports, ``.steering`` completeness,\n   170\t    # diff review trail) apply uniformly.\n   171\t    tool_input = payload.get(\"tool_input\")\n   172\t    if isinstance(tool_input, dict):\n   173\t        command = tool_input.get(\"command\")\n   174\t        if isinstance(command, str) and \"*** Begin Patch\" not in command:\n   175\t            impl_shell_targets: list[str] = []\n   176\t            for raw_path in shell_write_targets(command):\n   177\t                rel = relative_path(root, raw_path)\n   178\t                if is_impl_path(rel):\n   179\t                    impl_shell_targets.append(rel)\n   180\t            if impl_shell_targets:\n   181\t                preview = \", \".join(sorted(set(impl_shell_targets))[:3])\n   182\t                return deny(\n   183\t                    \"SH-1: shell-write into src/erre_sandbox/ is forbidden; \"\n   184\t                    \"use Edit/Write/apply_patch tools so the same policy \"\n   185\t                    f\"guards apply. Detected target(s): {preview}\"\n   186\t                )\n   187\t    normalized = {\n   188\t        relative_path(root, path): lines for path, lines in target_map(payload).items()\n   189\t    }\n   190\t    if not normalized:\n   191\t        return 0\n   192\t    impl_targets = [path for path in normalized if is_impl_path(path)]\n   193\t    if impl_targets:\n   194\t        status = task_status(latest_task(root))\n   195\t        if status[\"task\"] is None:\n   196\t            return deny(\n   197\t                \"Implementation edits require a recent .steering/YYYYMMDD-task directory \"\n   198\t                \"with requirement.md, design.md, and tasklist.md.\"\n   199\t            )\n   200\t        if status[\"missing\"]:\n   201\t            return deny(\n   202\t                f\"Implementation edits require complete steering files; missing: \"\n   203\t                f\"{', '.join(status['missing'])}.\"\n   204\t            )\n   205\t    for path, lines in normalized.items():\n   206\t        violation = check_banned(path, lines)\n   207\t        if violation:\n   208\t            return deny(violation)\n   209\t    return 0\n   210\t\n   211\t\n   212\tif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n   213\t    raise SystemExit(main())\n"}}
.steering/20260515-security-hardening-pre-m10-followup/codex-review.stderr:6149:/Users/johnd/.codex/sessions/2026/05/15/rollout-2026-05-15T18-02-57-019e2adf-e667-7241-b4b7-edcb4561a395.jsonl:68:{"timestamp":"2026-05-15T09:04:00.408Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"function_call_output","call_id":"call_f6dR93F5ZbnOS5s3H5ZugfNS","output":"Chunk ID: adf004\nWall time: 0.0000 seconds\nProcess exited with code 0\nOriginal token count: 450\nOutput:\n     1\t{\n     2\t  \"hooks\": {\n     3\t    \"SessionStart\": [\n     4\t      {\n     5\t        \"matcher\": \"startup|resume|clear\",\n     6\t        \"hooks\": [\n     7\t          {\n     8\t            \"type\": \"command\",\n     9\t            \"command\": \"/usr/bin/python3 \\\"$(git rev-parse --show-toplevel)/.codex/hooks/session_start.py\\\"\",\n    10\t            \"timeout\": 10,\n    11\t            \"statusMessage\": \"Loading ERRE Codex context\"\n    12\t          }\n    13\t        ]\n    14\t      }\n    15\t    ],\n    16\t    \"UserPromptSubmit\": [\n    17\t      {\n    18\t        \"hooks\": [\n    19\t          {\n    20\t            \"type\": \"command\",\n    21\t            \"command\": \"/usr/bin/python3 \\\"$(git rev-parse --show-toplevel)/.codex/hooks/user_prompt_submit.py\\\"\",\n    22\t            \"timeout\": 10,\n    23\t            \"statusMessage\": \"Checking ERRE task context\"\n    24\t          }\n    25\t        ]\n    26\t      }\n    27\t    ],\n    28\t    \"PreToolUse\": [\n    29\t      {\n    30\t        \"matcher\": \"apply_patch|Edit|Write|exec_command|Bash\",\n    31\t        \"hooks\": [\n    32\t          {\n    33\t            \"type\": \"command\",\n    34\t            \"command\": \"/usr/bin/python3 \\\"$(git rev-parse --show-toplevel)/.codex/hooks/pre_tool_use_policy.py\\\"\",\n    35\t            \"timeout\": 10,\n    36\t            \"statusMessage\": \"Checking ERRE edit policy\"\n    37\t          }\n    38\t        ]\n    39\t      }\n    40\t    ],\n    41\t    \"Stop\": [\n    42\t      {\n    43\t        \"hooks\": [\n    44\t          {\n    45\t            \"type\": \"command\",\n    46\t            \"command\": \"/usr/bin/python3 \\\"$(git rev-parse --show-toplevel)/.codex/hooks/stop_report.py\\\"\",\n    47\t            \"timeout\": 60,\n    48\t            \"statusMessage\": \"Running ERRE stop checks\"\n    49\t          }\n    50\t        ]\n    51\t      }\n    52\t    ]\n    53\t  }\n    54\t}\n"}}
.steering/20260515-security-hardening-pre-m10-followup/codex-review.stderr:6150:/Users/johnd/.codex/sessions/2026/05/15/rollout-2026-05-15T18-02-57-019e2adf-e667-7241-b4b7-edcb4561a395.jsonl:69:{"timestamp":"2026-05-15T09:04:00.408Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"function_call_output","call_id":"call_NANI42enzo36bcxCCtom2LY3","output":"Chunk ID: f28e5f\nWall time: 0.0000 seconds\nProcess exited with code 0\nOriginal token count: 2084\nOutput:\n     1\t\"\"\"SH-1 red-team tests for the ``pre_tool_use_policy.py`` Codex hook.\n     2\t\n     3\tThe hook gates ``exec_command`` / ``Bash`` tool calls that would write into\n     4\t``src/erre_sandbox/`` via shell redirects, ``sed -i``, ``tee``, heredocs,\n     5\tor inline Python literals. Each case below invokes the hook as a fresh\n     6\tsubprocess with a synthetic Codex-style payload on stdin and asserts the\n     7\thook emits the JSON ``permissionDecision=\"deny\"`` envelope (the canonical\n     8\tCodex hook protocol; the helper-level ``deny()`` returns exit 0 with the\n     9\tstructured stdout so downstream telemetry stays parseable).\n    10\t\"\"\"\n    11\t\n    12\tfrom __future__ import annotations\n    13\t\n    14\timport json\n    15\timport subprocess\n    16\timport sys\n    17\tfrom pathlib import Path\n    18\tfrom typing import Any\n    19\t\n    20\timport pytest\n    21\t\n    22\tREPO_ROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[2]\n    23\tHOOK_PATH = REPO_ROOT / \".codex\" / \"hooks\" / \"pre_tool_use_policy.py\"\n    24\t\n    25\t\n    26\tdef _invoke_hook(payload: dict[str, Any]) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    27\t    \"\"\"Run the hook as a fresh subprocess and parse its JSON stdout.\n    28\t\n    29\t    The hook contract is ``exit 0`` + JSON ``permissionDecision`` envelope\n    30\t    in stdout (Codex protocol). The subprocess is run with the project\n    31\t    repo root as CWD so ``repo_root`` / ``latest_task`` resolve to the\n    32\t    live ``.steering/`` tree and the SH-1 guard fires on its own merit\n    33\t    rather than via the ``.steering`` completeness fallback.\n    34\t    \"\"\"\n    35\t    result = subprocess.run(  # noqa: S603 — fixed argv to the in-repo hook\n    36\t        [sys.executable, str(HOOK_PATH)],\n    37\t        input=json.dumps(payload),\n    38\t        capture_output=True,\n    39\t        text=True,\n    40\t        timeout=10,\n    41\t        cwd=str(REPO_ROOT),\n    42\t        check=False,\n    43\t    )\n    44\t    assert result.returncode == 0, (\n    45\t        f\"hook returncode={result.returncode}\\n\"\n    46\t        f\"stderr={result.stderr}\\nstdout={result.stdout}\"\n    47\t    )\n    48\t    stdout = result.stdout.strip()\n    49\t    if not stdout:\n    50\t        # Allow path: ``main()`` returns 0 without writing to stdout when no\n    51\t        # rule fires. Tests checking benign commands should see this branch.\n    52\t        return {}\n    53\t    try:\n    54\t        return json.loads(stdout)\n    55\t    except json.JSONDecodeError as exc:  # pragma: no cover — diagnostic only\n    56\t        pytest.fail(f\"hook stdout not JSON: {stdout!r} (err={exc})\")\n    57\t\n    58\t\n    59\tdef _assert_deny(envelope: dict[str, Any], *, contains: str) -> None:\n    60\t    \"\"\"Helper: assert the hook envelope is a deny mentioning ``contains``.\"\"\"\n    61\t    hook_output = envelope.get(\"hookSpecificOutput\", {})\n    62\t    assert hook_output.get(\"permissionDecision\") == \"deny\", envelope\n    63\t    reason = hook_output.get(\"permissionDecisionReason\", \"\")\n    64\t    assert contains in reason, (\n    65\t        f\"expected deny reason to mention {contains!r}, got {reason!r}\"\n    66\t    )\n    67\t\n    68\t\n    69\t# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n    70\t# Red-team: 5 canonical shell-write techniques the hook must block.\n    71\t# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n    72\t\n    73\t\n    74\tdef test_sed_in_place_into_impl_is_denied() -> None:\n    75\t    \"\"\"``sed -i`` rewriting an impl file is denied (in-place edit bypass).\"\"\"\n    76\t    payload = {\n    77\t        \"tool\": \"exec_command\",\n    78\t        \"tool_input\": {\n    79\t            \"command\": (\n    80\t                \"sed -i 's/from typing/from typing\\\\nimport openai/' \"\n    81\t                \"src/erre_sandbox/inference/sglang_adapter.py\"\n    82\t            ),\n    83\t        },\n    84\t        \"cwd\": str(REPO_ROOT),\n    85\t    }\n    86\t    envelope = _invoke_hook(payload)\n    87\t    _assert_deny(envelope, contains=\"SH-1\")\n    88\t\n    89\t\n    90\tdef test_echo_append_into_impl_is_denied() -> None:\n    91\t    \"\"\"``echo \"...\" >> PATH`` redirected into an impl file is denied.\"\"\"\n    92\t    payload = {\n    93\t        \"tool\": \"exec_command\",\n    94\t        \"tool_input\": {\n    95\t            \"command\": ('echo \"import bpy\" >> src/erre_sandbox/world/tick.py'),\n    96\t        },\n    97\t        \"cwd\": str(REPO_ROOT),\n    98\t    }\n    99\t    envelope = _invoke_hook(payload)\n   100\t    _assert_deny(envelope, contains=\"SH-1\")\n   101\t\n   102\t\n   103\tdef test_tee_into_impl_is_denied() -> None:\n   104\t    \"\"\"``tee PATH`` writing to an impl file is denied (even with empty stdin).\"\"\"\n   105\t    payload = {\n   106\t        \"tool\": \"exec_command\",\n   107\t        \"tool_input\": {\n   108\t            \"command\": \"tee src/erre_sandbox/x.py < /dev/null\",\n   109\t        },\n   110\t        \"cwd\": str(REPO_ROOT),\n   111\t    }\n   112\t    envelope = _invoke_hook(payload)\n   113\t    _assert_deny(envelope, contains=\"SH-1\")\n   114\t\n   115\t\n   116\tdef test_python_dash_c_open_write_into_impl_is_denied() -> None:\n   117\t    \"\"\"``python -c \"open(PATH, 'w').write(...)\"`` is denied.\"\"\"\n   118\t    payload = {\n   119\t        \"tool\": \"exec_command\",\n   120\t        \"tool_input\": {\n   121\t            \"command\": (\n   122\t                \"python -c \\\"open('src/erre_sandbox/y.py','w').write('print(1)')\\\"\"\n   123\t            ),\n   124\t        },\n   125\t        \"cwd\": str(REPO_ROOT),\n   126\t    }\n   127\t    envelope = _invoke_hook(payload)\n   128\t    _assert_deny(envelope, contains=\"SH-1\")\n   129\t\n   130\t\n   131\tdef test_cat_heredoc_into_impl_is_denied() -> None:\n   132\t    \"\"\"``cat > PATH << EOF ... EOF`` heredoc into an impl file is denied.\"\"\"\n   133\t    payload = {\n   134\t        \"tool\": \"exec_command\",\n   135\t        \"tool_input\": {\n   136\t            \"command\": (\"cat > src/erre_sandbox/z.py <<EOF\\nimport anthropic\\nEOF\"),\n   137\t        },\n   138\t        \"cwd\": str(REPO_ROOT),\n   139\t    }\n   140\t    envelope = _invoke_hook(payload)\n   141\t    _assert_deny(envelope, contains=\"SH-1\")\n   142\t\n   143\t\n   144\t# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n   145\t# Negative path: benign shell commands must NOT be denied by the SH-1 gate.\n   146\t# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n   147\t\n   148\t\n   149\tdef test_grep_into_impl_is_allowed() -> None:\n   150\t    \"\"\"Read-only ``grep src/erre_sandbox/...`` does not match write patterns.\"\"\"\n   151\t    payload = {\n   152\t        \"tool\": \"exec_command\",\n   153\t        \"tool_input\": {\n   154\t            \"command\": \"grep -rn 'WorldRuntime' src/erre_sandbox/world\",\n   155\t        },\n   156\t        \"cwd\": str(REPO_ROOT),\n   157\t    }\n   158\t    envelope = _invoke_hook(payload)\n   159\t    # No write into impl → empty target_map → main() returns 0 with empty\n   160\t    # stdout. JSON parse of an empty stdout raises — handle that fall-back.\n   161\t    hook_output = envelope.get(\"hookSpecificOutput\") if envelope else None\n   162\t    if hook_output is not None:\n   163\t        # If the hook emitted anything, it must NOT be a deny for SH-1.\n   164\t        decision = hook_output.get(\"permissionDecision\")\n   165\t        if decision == \"deny\":\n   166\t            reason = hook_output.get(\"permissionDecisionReason\", \"\")\n   167\t            assert \"SH-1\" not in reason, (\n   168\t                \"grep read-only command must not trip the SH-1 shell-write guard\"\n   169\t            )\n   170\t\n   171\t\n   172\tdef test_shell_write_outside_impl_is_allowed() -> None:\n   173\t    \"\"\"Writing to /tmp or var/ via shell is allowed (not in src/erre_sandbox/).\"\"\"\n   174\t    payload = {\n   175\t        \"tool\": \"exec_command\",\n   176\t        \"tool_input\": {\n   177\t            \"command\": 'echo \"junk\" > /tmp/scratch.txt',\n   178\t        },\n   179\t        \"cwd\": str(REPO_ROOT),\n   180\t    }\n   181\t    envelope = _invoke_hook(payload)\n   182\t    hook_output = envelope.get(\"hookSpecificOutput\") if envelope else None\n   183\t    if hook_output is not None:\n   184\t        decision = hook_output.get(\"permissionDecision\")\n   185\t        if decision == \"deny\":\n   186\t            reason = hook_output.get(\"permissionDecisionReason\", \"\")\n   187\t            assert \"SH-1\" not in reason, (\n   188\t                \"shell-write to /tmp must not trip the SH-1 src/erre_sandbox/ guard\"\n   189\t            )\n"}}
.steering/20260515-security-hardening-pre-m10-followup/codex-review.stderr:6151:/Users/johnd/.codex/sessions/2026/05/15/rollout-2026-05-15T18-02-57-019e2adf-e667-7241-b4b7-edcb4561a395.jsonl:96:{"timestamp":"2026-05-15T09:04:27.715Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"function_call_output","call_id":"call_dQTrV9Tl2CM9LXZhp4JxKHr4","output":"Chunk ID: af334f\nWall time: 0.0000 seconds\nProcess exited with code 0\nOriginal token count: 2540\nOutput:\n     1\t# 設計判断 — security-hardening-pre-m10-followup\n     2\t\n     3\t本 task は **親 task `.steering/20260513-security-hardening-pre-m10/decisions.md` の SH-1 / SH-2 ADR をそのまま実装する** ため、新 ADR を立てない。以下は親 ADR の verbatim 引用 (linkback 付き) + 開始時 fact-check の記録 + 本 task 中に発生した implementation-level 判断 (ADR addendum 形式)。\n     4\t\n     5\t---\n     6\t\n     7\t## SH-1 (親 task verbatim 引用) — Hook + CI shell-bypass defense\n     8\t\n     9\tSource: `.steering/20260513-security-hardening-pre-m10/decisions.md` SH-1\n    10\t\n    11\t- **判断日時**: 2026-05-13\n    12\t- **背景**: `codex_issue.md` §1 HIGH。`.codex/hooks.json:28-39` matcher が `apply_patch|Edit|Write` のみ、`exec_command` 経由の shell 書き込みが `.steering` completeness guard / banned import check を通過する。\n    13\t- **選択肢**:\n    14\t  - A: hook matcher 拡張のみ (`exec_command|Bash` 追加)\n    15\t  - B: CI grep gate 追加のみ (`policy-grep-gate` job)\n    16\t  - **C**: hook + CI の両層\n    17\t- **採用**: **C**\n    18\t- **理由**:\n    19\t  - hook 単独 (A) は `apply_patch` 偽装で素通り、bypass risk が残る\n    20\t  - CI 単独 (B) は feedback latency が遅い (PR push 後)、IDE 内即時 deny の UX を失う\n    21\t  - 両層 (C) は既存 `eval-egress-grep-gate` (`ci.yml:83-137`) が同型パターンとして validated、defense-in-depth 完成\n    22\t- **トレードオフ**: 開発時の hook 誤検知 (false positive) リスク増。red-team test 5 ケースで pattern 妥当性を担保\n    23\t- **影響範囲**: `.codex/hooks/` + `.github/workflows/ci.yml` + 新規 `tests/test_codex_hooks/`\n    24\t- **見直しタイミング**: red-team test で誤検知率 >5% に達した場合、または CI grep gate が M9-eval / m9-c-spike 系の正当なツール使用をブロックした場合\n    25\t\n    26\t---\n    27\t\n    28\t## SH-2 (親 task verbatim 引用) — WebSocket 3-layer auth (token + Origin + cap)\n    29\t\n    30\tSource: `.steering/20260513-security-hardening-pre-m10/decisions.md` SH-2\n    31\t\n    32\t- **判断日時**: 2026-05-13\n    33\t- **背景**: `codex_issue.md` §2 MEDIUM。`__main__.py:73-74` / `bootstrap.py:70-71` default `0.0.0.0:8000`、`integration/gateway.py:501-652` `ws_observe()` に認証 / Origin / session cap いずれもなし。Mac↔G-GEAR LAN rsync workflow は LAN 内前提だが、共有 Wi-Fi 誤公開時の blast radius が無制限。\n    34\t- **選択肢** (Plan agent enumeration + AskUserQuestion):\n    35\t  - **A. Token rollout: back-compat 優先** (`require_token=False` default、Godot patch を別 PR、enforce は後続)\n    36\t  - B. Token rollout: 同一 PR 強制 (P4 で Godot WS client patch も含める)\n    37\t  - C. Token rollout: Godot 免除 list (loopback の Godot は token 不要)\n    38\t- **採用**: **A** (ユーザー選択、2026-05-13 AskUserQuestion)\n    39\t- **理由**:\n    40\t  - A は blast radius 最小 (Godot 未パッチでも continue)、PR 単位の独立性高い\n    41\t  - B は Godot patch を blocker 化、本 PR scope 拡大 + Godot live test 必要で工数 +5h\n    42\t  - C は認証ロジック分岐増、SH-2 の \"3 layer independent\" 原則を破る\n    43\t- **トレードオフ**: A 採用で token 機構は **存在するが強制しない** 初期状態、別 PR で `require_token=True` default 化が必要。記録: `tasklist.md` に follow-up task 起票\n    44\t- **追加判断**:\n    45\t  - **`MAX_ACTIVE_SESSIONS = 8`** (Mac+G-GEAR Godot + curl + slack + M10 per-persona UI × 3、4 では tight、16 は memory waste で却下、AskUserQuestion 結果)\n    46\t  - **Token storage**: file `var/secrets/ws_token` primary + env `ERRE_WS_TOKEN` fallback + explicit `--ws-token` arg は test のみ (`ps -E` leak 回避)\n    47\t  - **Origin allowlist**: 空 list ⇒ check disabled (Godot native WS empty Origin 対応)、`host=0.0.0.0` + empty origin + `require_token=False` は startup error で誤公開予防\n    48\t- **棄却**:\n    49\t  - mTLS (運用負荷過大、cert rotate 必要)\n    50\t  - cookie auth (Godot native WS が cookie 非対応)\n    51\t  - `127.0.0.1` 強制 (Mac↔G-GEAR LAN rsync workflow 実害)\n    52\t- **影響範囲**: `__main__.py` / `bootstrap.py` / `integration/gateway.py` / `integration/protocol.py` / `docs/architecture.md` / `README.md` / `docs/development-guidelines.md` / `tests/test_integration/test_gateway.py`\n    53\t- **見直しタイミング**:\n    54\t  - Godot 4.4 WS client が token 対応した時点で `require_token=True` default 化の follow-up PR\n    55\t  - `MAX_ACTIVE_SESSIONS=8` が M11 で不足判明した場合、cap 値 reopen\n    56\t  - LAN 外公開要件が発生した場合 (M14+? OSF 公開時)、mTLS 検討\n    57\t\n    58\t---\n    59\t\n    60\t## SH-FOLLOWUP-1 — `deny()` exit code 解釈の確定\n    61\t\n    62\t- **判断日時**: 2026-05-15 (本 task 開始時 fact-check)\n    63\t- **背景**: 起点プロンプト `.steering/20260513-security-hardening-pre-m10/next-session-prompt-followup.md` Step 3 の hook smoke 検証で「exit 2 + deny message」を期待していたが、実機 `pre_tool_use_policy.py:37` の `deny()` は **exit 0 + JSON `permissionDecision:\"deny\"`** を返す (Codex 公式 hook protocol)。\n    64\t- **選択肢** (AskUserQuestion):\n    65\t  - **A**: JSON deny を維持、smoke 検証を JSON match に修正 (Recommended、ユーザー採用)\n    66\t  - B: `deny()` を return 2 に変更 + JSON も併用\n    67\t  - C: プロンプト通り exit 2 のみ (JSON 廃止)\n    68\t- **採用**: **A**\n    69\t- **理由**:\n    70\t  - 現実装は Codex 公式 `permissionDecision: \"deny\"` JSON 構造を採用、reason 文字列が structured で telemetry 親和性が高い\n    71\t  - B は二重化だが既存 `deny()` 呼出箇所 (4 箇所) の挙動は実用上変わらず、変更 cost に見合わない\n    72\t  - C は structured reason を捨てる退行\n    73\t- **トレードオフ**: hook smoke 検証手順がプロンプト本文と異なる (`jq -e '.hookSpecificOutput.permissionDecision == \"deny\"'`)。本 ADR で記録、Codex 14th review prompt にも明記\n    74\t- **影響範囲**: `tests/test_codex_hooks/test_shell_bypass_policy.py` の assert は stdout JSON match、`.steering/20260513-security-hardening-pre-m10/next-session-prompt-followup.md` Step 3 hook smoke 行は本 task 後 stale 化 (修正不要、`git rm next-session-prompt.md` 同梱で発生する `next-session-prompt-followup.md` も同様に close 時に処理判定)\n    75\t- **見直しタイミング**: Codex CLI の hook protocol が future version で exit code based に強制移行した場合\n    76\t\n    77\t---\n    78\t\n    79\t## SH-FOLLOWUP-2 — CI policy-grep-gate の T201 backstop 設計\n    80\t\n    81\t- **判断日時**: 2026-05-15 (本 task 開始時 fact-check)\n    82\t- **背景**: 親 task design-final.md L67 で `grep -rnE '^\\s*print\\s*\\(' src/erre_sandbox/` を T201 backstop として設計していたが、Bash fact-check で `src/erre_sandbox/inference/ollama_adapter.py:145` に既存の **noqa なし raw print()** が存在することが判明。CI は現状 green なので ruff 側に何らかの allow 経路がある (file-level skip or pyproject extra exemption の可能性)。\n    83\t- **選択肢** (AskUserQuestion):\n    84\t  - **A**: ruff と同等の例外 (cli/** 除外 + 行 noqa 尊重) — `uv run ruff check --select T201 src/erre_sandbox` 再実行で代替 (Recommended、ユーザー採用)\n    85\t  - B: 厳格 grep で全 print() を block (既存 `ollama_adapter.py:145` も対象、本 PR で `# noqa: T201` 追加か `logger.debug` 置換必要)\n    86\t  - C: print rule は CI grep から外す、import 禁止と `.steering` completeness のみ grep\n    87\t- **採用**: **A**\n    88\t- **理由**:\n    89\t  - 既存 CI green を破壊しない (retro-active breakage なし)\n    90\t  - ruff exemption は pyproject + per-line noqa で集約管理、CI grep で重複 enforce すると drift risk\n    91\t  - SH-1 design-final.md L67 「ruff T201 の backstop」要件は、grep ではなく ruff 自身の冪等再実行でも満たされる (CI 内別 job で実行 = backstop)\n    92\t- **トレードオフ**: 厳格 grep より弱い (\"ruff 自身の bug\" が backstop で検出できない)。ruff version pin と CI step 順序で品質保証\n    93\t- **影響範囲**: `.github/workflows/ci.yml` `policy-grep-gate` job の print step は `uv run ruff check --select T201 src/erre_sandbox` に。grep は openai/anthropic + bpy + `.steering` completeness のみ\n    94\t- **見直しタイミング**: ruff `T201` が future version で削除 / rename された場合、または `ollama_adapter.py:145` を本来正しく block すべき判断が後日発生した場合 (別 task で audit)\n    95\t\n    96\t---\n    97\t\n    98\t## SH-FOLLOWUP-3 — (placeholder)\n    99\t\n   100\tCodex 14th review で MEDIUM 切出時にここに ADR addendum を追加する。\n   101\t\n   102\t---\n   103\t\n   104\t## Mac↔G-GEAR LAN smoke 手順 (P4d 必須、SH-2 ADR の見直しタイミングに関連)\n   105\t\n   106\t`require_token=False` default で既存 rsync workflow が不変であることを実機で確認:\n   107\t\n   108\t```bash\n   109\t# Mac 側 (本 PR の branch)\n   110\tuv run python -m erre_sandbox --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000 \\\n   111\t  --personas study/peripatos --check-ollama false &\n   112\tSERVER_PID=$!\n   113\tsleep 3\n   114\t\n   115\t# G-GEAR 側 (curl で WS handshake without token)\n   116\tcurl -i -N \\\n   117\t  -H \"Connection: Upgrade\" -H \"Upgrade: websocket\" \\\n   118\t  -H \"Sec-WebSocket-Key: dGhlIHNhbXBsZSBub25jZQ==\" \\\n   119\t  -H \"Sec-WebSocket-Version: 13\" \\\n   120\t  http://mac.local:8000/observe\n   121\t# Expected: 101 Switching Protocols (require_token=False なので token 不要)\n   122\t\n   123\tkill $SERVER_PID\n   124\t```\n   125\t\n   126\t本 smoke は手動。`tests/test_integration/test_gateway.py::TestWebSocketAuth::test_back_compat_no_token_required_by_default` で代替自動化済 (single-host TestClient 経由)。\n"}}
.steering/20260515-security-hardening-pre-m10-followup/codex-review.stderr:6156:/Users/johnd/.codex/sessions/2026/05/15/rollout-2026-05-15T16-24-14-019e2a85-861b-7152-9e58-45e3defa548d.jsonl:38:{"timestamp":"2026-05-15T07:25:00.354Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"function_call_output","call_id":"call_6EBn0inL3D5aEyGXr3089MyE","output":"Chunk ID: e258ca\nWall time: 0.0000 seconds\nProcess exited with code 0\nOriginal token count: 2225\nOutput:\n# 設計 — security-hardening-pre-m10 (v1 initial draft)\n\n承認済み plan `/Users/johnd/.claude/plans/agile-chasing-sifakis.md` をもとに、\n`.steering/_template/design.md` 構造で詳細化した v1。**次ステップで `/reimagine`\nを §2 (WS token+Origin+cap) + §5 (queue split) のみ適用** し、v2 と比較して\n`design-final.md` に確定する。\n\n## 実装アプローチ\n\nCodex 12th review 5 件を **defense-in-depth × M9 baseline 不可侵** の二軸で消化する。\n\n- **defense-in-depth**: §1 hook + CI / §2 token + Origin + cap / §3 network split /\n  §4 path validation / §5 queue bound の **3 層独立** 化\n- **M9 baseline 不可侵**: `data/eval/golden/` 30 cells + `src/erre_sandbox/evidence/`\n  には触れない、`SCHEMA_VERSION` (`schemas.py:44` `\"0.10.0-m7h\"`) 不変\n- **back-compat 優先**: WS token は `require_token=False` default、`/tmp/p3a_natural_*`\n  default path 維持、`0.0.0.0` host default 据置 (Mac↔G-GEAR LAN rsync 保護)\n\n各 finding は独立 commit、最終 1 PR squash で M10 着手前の baseline 完成。\n\n## 変更対象\n\n### 修正するファイル\n\n**§1 hook + CI** (CI が最終防衛線、hook は first-line nuisance filter)\n- `.codex/hooks.json:28-39` — `PreToolUse` matcher を `apply_patch|Edit|Write|exec_command|Bash` に拡張 (~5 行)\n- `.codex/hooks/pre_tool_use_policy.py` — 新 helper `shell_write_targets(command)` (~50 行)、`.steering` completeness guard を shell 経路でも発火\n- `.github/workflows/ci.yml` — 新 job `policy-grep-gate` を `eval-egress-grep-gate` (L83-137) の下に (~30 行)、ruff `T201` の backstop + `.steering` completeness check\n\n**§2 WS auth** (3-layer independent: token + Origin + cap)\n- `src/erre_sandbox/integration/protocol.py:52` 近傍 — `DEFAULT_ALLOWED_ORIGINS` + `MAX_ACTIVE_SESSIONS=8` を `Final` constant で追加 (~10 行)\n- `src/erre_sandbox/integration/gateway.py:194-202` — `Registry.add()` を `reserve_slot()` / `release_slot()` に置換 (~20 行)、cap 超過時 `SessionCapExceededError` raise\n- `src/erre_sandbox/integration/gateway.py:518-552` — `ws_observe()` の `accept()` (L545) 前に Origin/token/cap check を挿入 (~30 行)、close code 1008 (policy) / 1013 (try-again-later)\n- `src/erre_sandbox/bootstrap.py:70-71` — `BootConfig` に `ws_token` / `require_token` / `allowed_origins` / `max_sessions` field 追加、`_resolve_ws_token()` helper (~30 行)\n- `src/erre_sandbox/__main__.py:73-74` — `--ws-token` / `--require-token` / `--allowed-origins` / `--max-sessions` CLI flag 追加 (~15 行)\n\n**§3 Codex network** (1-line config + doc)\n- `.codex/config.toml:10` — `network_access = true` → `false`\n- `.codex/config.toml:4` — `web_search = \"live\"` **据置** (decoupled feature)\n- `AGENTS.md` — 新セクション \"Network access policy\"、SGLang v0.3+ multi-LoRA 発見実績 citation\n- `.agents/skills/erre-workflow/SKILL.md` — 同ノート (machine-readable)\n\n**§4 eval CLI path guard**\n- `src/erre_sandbox/cli/eval_run_golden.py:711-775` 近傍 — `_resolve_memory_db_path()` helper + `ALLOWED_MEMORY_DB_PREFIXES` (~50 行)\n- `src/erre_sandbox/cli/eval_run_golden.py:1029-1030` — unconditional unlink を helper 経由に\n- `src/erre_sandbox/cli/eval_run_golden.py:1269-1292` — 既存 `--overwrite` 3-flag パターンに `--overwrite-memory-db` 追加\n\n**§5 runtime queue**\n- `src/erre_sandbox/world/tick.py:386` — `_envelopes` 単一 unbounded を `_heartbeat_envelopes` (maxsize=1 coalesce) + `_envelopes` (maxsize=1024 drop-oldest) の 2-queue に分割 (~10 行)\n- `src/erre_sandbox/world/tick.py:722` — `inject_envelope()` の `put_nowait` を drop-oldest + ErrorMsg `runtime_backlog_overflow` warning に (~15 行)\n- `src/erre_sandbox/world/tick.py:1271` — heartbeat 経路を coalesce 化 (~10 行)\n- `src/erre_sandbox/world/tick.py:1340` — `_consume_result` も §5-2 と同型 (~15 行)\n- `src/erre_sandbox/world/tick.py` `recv_envelope` — 2-queue race-merge (FIFO within priority class) (~20 行)\n\n**Doc**\n- `docs/architecture.md:330` — 「認証なし (LAN 内前提)」を「shared-token (opt-in) + Origin allow-list + session cap (LAN 内前提)」に\n- `docs/development-guidelines.md` — `var/secrets/ws_token` rotate 運用ノート\n- `README.md` — `mkdir -p var/secrets && chmod 700 var/secrets` 初回 provisioning 手順\n\n### 新規作成するファイル\n\n- `tests/test_codex_hooks/__init__.py`\n- `tests/test_codex_hooks/test_shell_bypass_policy.py` — red-team 5 ケース\n- `.steering/20260513-security-hardening-pre-m10/decisions.md` — ADR `SH-1`〜`SH-5`\n- `.steering/20260513-security-hardening-pre-m10/codex-review-prompt.md` — Codex 13th 入力\n- `.steering/20260513-security-hardening-pre-m10/codex-review.md` — Codex 13th verbatim 保存\n- `.steering/20260513-security-hardening-pre-m10/design-final.md` — /reimagine 後の確定版\n\n### 削除するファイル\n\nなし。M9 baseline 不可侵。\n\n## 影響範囲\n\n| 領域 | 影響 | 対処 |\n|---|---|---|\n| Mac↔G-GEAR LAN rsync workflow | `require_token=False` default で **無影響** | tasklist で smoke 検証 |\n| Godot 4.4 WS client | Origin/token 未対応の場合、loopback 経由は変更なし | empty Origin 受容 if-branch を実装時 audit |\n| M9-eval golden baseline | **完全に触らない** | CI に `git diff origin/main..HEAD -- data/eval/golden` 検証 |\n| existing pytest suite | gateway / tick / cli の signature 互換維持 | `Registry.add()` deprecation 経由で 1 リリース cycle 移行 |\n| schema 互換 | `SCHEMA_VERSION` 不変、`ErrorMsg` の新 code `\"runtime_backlog_overflow\"` を流用 | schema bump 回避 |\n\n## 既存パターンとの整合性\n\n- **§2 reject-before-accept**: `gateway.py:523-543` の subscribe parse error path と同型\n- **§2 drop-oldest + ErrorMsg warning**: `gateway.py:208-258` `Registry.fan_out` の既存実装 (helper `_make_error` も同所)\n- **§4 path validation**: `cli/eval_run_golden.py:711-775` `_resolve_output_paths` の `.tmp` cleanup pattern\n- **§4 3-flag escalation**: `cli/eval_run_golden.py:1269-1292` `--overwrite` / `--allow-partial-rescue` / `--force-rescue`\n- **§5 bounded queue**: `integration/protocol.py:52` `MAX_ENVELOPE_BACKLOG = 256` の `Final[int]` 配置\n- **§1 grep gate**: `.github/workflows/ci.yml:83-137` `eval-egress-grep-gate` の job 構造\n- **§1 deny pattern**: `.codex/hooks/pre_tool_use_policy.py:11-24` の既存 deny rule set\n\n## テスト戦略\n\n### 単体テスト (新規 + 既存拡張)\n\n- **§1**: `tests/test_codex_hooks/test_shell_bypass_policy.py` 5 ケース (sed/echo/tee/python-c/heredoc)\n- **§2**: `tests/test_integration/test_gateway.py` 拡張 6 ケース (token miss/mismatch/match、origin reject、cap close 1013、back-compat default)\n- **§4**: `tests/test_cli/test_eval_run_golden.py` 拡張 4 ケース (symlink/prefix/exists/overwrite)\n- **§5**: `tests/test_world/test_runtime_lifecycle.py` 拡張 2 ケース (overflow warning、heartbeat coalesce)\n\n### 統合テスト\n\n- 既存 `test_gateway.py:193-210` `test_fan_out_drops_oldest_*` が runtime 側でも green を維持\n- 既存 `test_multi_agent_stream.py` が token=None default で green\n\n### E2E\n\n- **Mac↔G-GEAR LAN smoke**: 手動 (decisions.md に手順記録)、`require_token=False` で\n  既存 rsync workflow 不変を確認。token rotation の opt-in 検証は別 PR (Godot 4.4\n  WS client patch が前提)\n- **Codex hook smoke**: `echo '{...}' | uv run python .codex/hooks/pre_tool_use_policy.py` で\n  deny 確認\n\n## ロールバック計画\n\n- §1: `.codex/hooks.json` matcher を `apply_patch|Edit|Write` に戻す (single commit revert)\n- §2: `require_token=False` default なので enforce していない、`bootstrap.py` の\n  config 削除 + `gateway.py` の auth gate コメントアウトで back-out\n- §3: `.codex/config.toml` の `network_access` を `true` に戻す (1-line revert)\n- §4: `_resolve_memory_db_path` を削除、L1029-1030 の unconditional unlink に戻す\n- §5: `_envelopes` を `asyncio.Queue()` (unbounded) に戻す、`_heartbeat_envelopes` 削除\n\n全 §i は独立 revert 可能。一括 PR を merge 後に問題発生時は **finding 単位で\nrevert PR** を出す方針。\n\n## /reimagine 適用範囲 (次ステップ)\n\n| § | /reimagine 適用 | 理由 |\n|---|---|---|\n| §1 hook + CI | **No** | CI grep gate は既存 `eval-egress-grep-gate` の port、単一案 |\n| §2 WS auth | **Yes** | token 方式 / Origin allowlist 粒度 / cap 計算で複数案 |\n| §3 Codex network | **No** | 1-line config 変更、単一案 |\n| §4 path guard | **No** | 既存 `--overwrite` 3-flag パターンの port、単一案 |\n| §5 queue split | **Yes** | 1-queue vs 2-queue vs 3-queue + drop policy で複数案 |\n\n§2 + §5 の /reimagine 結果と本 v1 案を比較して `design-final.md` で確定 → 実装着手。\n"}}
.steering/20260515-security-hardening-pre-m10-followup/codex-review.stderr:6157:/Users/johnd/.codex/sessions/2026/05/15/rollout-2026-05-15T16-24-14-019e2a85-861b-7152-9e58-45e3defa548d.jsonl:41:{"timestamp":"2026-05-15T07:25:00.399Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"function_call_output","call_id":"call_q0walA2AQUnWexO2ny4fRGHE","output":"Chunk ID: a47539\nWall time: 0.0000 seconds\nProcess exited with code 0\nOriginal token count: 2089\nOutput:\n# タスクリスト — security-hardening-pre-m10\n\nPlan: `/Users/johnd/.claude/plans/agile-chasing-sifakis.md`\nDesign-final: `design-final.md` (= `design.md` v1 を SH-0 prosess で昇格)\n\n## P0 — Scaffold (完了)\n\n- [x] [Mac] branch `feature/security-hardening-pre-m10` 作成\n- [x] [Mac] `requirement.md` 起草 (`codex_issue.md` 6 finding 統合、Path A 採用)\n- [x] [Mac] `design.md` v1 起草 (5 finding 詳細化、再利用パターン明示)\n- [x] [Mac] `decisions.md` ADR SH-0〜SH-5 起草 (SH-0 で /reimagine 代替プロセス明示)\n- [x] [Mac] `design-final.md` = design.md v1 昇格 (SH-0 判定)\n\n## P1 — §3 Codex network split (SH-3、~0.5h) — 完了\n\n- [x] [Mac] `.codex/config.toml:10` — `network_access = true` → `false`\n- [x] [Mac] `.codex/config.toml:4` — `web_search = \"live\"` 据置を確認\n- [x] [Mac] `AGENTS.md` — \"Network access policy\" section 追加\n  (SGLang v0.3+ multi-LoRA 発見実績 citation、per-session 明示承認運用)\n- [x] [Mac] `.agents/skills/erre-workflow/SKILL.md` — 同ノート追加\n- [x] [Mac] commit: `chore(codex): network_access=false split (SH-3)`\n\n## P2 — §4 `--memory-db` guard (SH-4、~2h) — 完了\n\n- [x] [Mac] `cli/eval_run_golden.py` — `ALLOWED_MEMORY_DB_PREFIX_STRINGS` + `_ALLOWED_MEMORY_DB_TMP_BASENAME_PREFIXES` constant 追加\n  (`/tmp/p3a_natural_` / `/tmp/erre-` / `var/eval/`)\n- [x] [Mac] `cli/eval_run_golden.py:711-775` 近傍 — `_resolve_memory_db_path()` helper 追加 + macOS `/tmp` → `/private/tmp` symlink 正規化対応\n  (symlink reject / prefix check / overwrite gate)\n- [x] [Mac] `cli/eval_run_golden.py:1029-1030` — unconditional unlink を helper 経由に\n- [x] [Mac] `cli/eval_run_golden.py:1269-1292` — `--overwrite-memory-db` flag 追加\n- [x] [Mac] `capture_natural()` signature — `overwrite_memory_db: bool = False` 追加 + caller `main()` で wire\n- [x] [Mac] `tests/test_cli/test_eval_run_golden.py` — 5 red-team ケース追加\n  (symlink / prefix / exists / overwrite / default auto-unlink)\n- [x] [Mac] `uv run pytest tests/test_cli/test_eval_run_golden.py -q -m eval` → 27 passed\n- [x] [Mac] 全 CI 緑確認 (`ruff check / format --check / mypy / pytest 1341 passed`)\n- [x] [Mac] commit: `feat(cli): eval --memory-db symlink+prefix+overwrite guard (SH-4)`\n\n## P3 — §5 bounded envelope queue + warning (SH-5、~3h)\n\n- [ ] [Mac] `world/tick.py:386` — `_envelopes` を 2-queue 分割\n  (`_heartbeat_envelopes` maxsize=1 + `_envelopes` maxsize=1024)\n- [ ] [Mac] `world/tick.py:722` `inject_envelope()` — drop-oldest + ErrorMsg\n  `runtime_backlog_overflow` warning (gateway L208-258 同型)\n- [ ] [Mac] `world/tick.py:1271` heartbeat 経路 — coalesce 化 (drain 旧 → push 新)\n- [ ] [Mac] `world/tick.py:1340` `_consume_result` — drop-oldest + warning\n- [ ] [Mac] `world/tick.py` `recv_envelope` — 2-queue race-merge (main 優先)\n- [ ] [Mac] `_make_error` helper の location 確定 (内部 vs 共通 utility 昇格、\n  Codex 13th review で再判断)\n- [ ] [Mac] `tests/test_world/test_runtime_lifecycle.py` — 2 ケース追加\n  (overflow warning / heartbeat coalesce)\n- [ ] [Mac] 既存 `runtime.drain_envelopes()` caller test の audit (mechanical 調整)\n- [ ] [Mac] `uv run pytest tests/test_world -q` 緑確認\n- [ ] [Mac] commit: `feat(world): bounded envelope queue + warning (SH-5)`\n\n## P4 — §2 WS auth (SH-2、~5h)\n\n### P4a — protocol + Registry\n\n- [ ] [Mac] `integration/protocol.py:52` 近傍 — `DEFAULT_ALLOWED_ORIGINS` + `MAX_ACTIVE_SESSIONS=8` constant 追加\n- [ ] [Mac] `integration/protocol.py` — `SessionCapExceededError` exception 追加\n- [ ] [Mac] `integration/gateway.py:194-202` — `Registry.add()` を `reserve_slot()` / `release_slot()` pair に置換\n\n### P4b — bootstrap + CLI\n\n- [ ] [Mac] `bootstrap.py:70-71` `BootConfig` — `ws_token` / `require_token` / `allowed_origins` / `max_sessions` field 追加\n- [ ] [Mac] `bootstrap.py` — `_resolve_ws_token()` helper (file → env → None)\n- [ ] [Mac] `__main__.py:73-74` — `--ws-token` / `--require-token` / `--allowed-origins` / `--max-sessions` flag 追加\n- [ ] [Mac] `host=0.0.0.0` + empty origin + `require_token=False` の startup error 実装\n\n### P4c — gateway integration\n\n- [ ] [Mac] `integration/gateway.py:518-552` — `accept()` 前に Origin/token/cap check 挿入\n  (subscribe parse error path L532-543 と同型)\n- [ ] [Mac] `finally` で `registry.release_slot(session_id)` 確実呼出\n\n### P4d — test + doc\n\n- [ ] [Mac] `tests/test_integration/test_gateway.py` — 6 ケース追加\n- [ ] [Mac] `docs/architecture.md:330` — 認証ポリシー更新\n- [ ] [Mac] `docs/development-guidelines.md` — token rotate 運用ノート\n- [ ] [Mac] `README.md` — `var/secrets/` provisioning 手順\n- [ ] [Mac] `uv run pytest tests/test_integration/test_gateway.py tests/test_integration/test_multi_agent_stream.py -q` 緑確認\n- [ ] [Mac] Mac↔G-GEAR LAN smoke (手動、`require_token=False` 確認、decisions.md に手順記録)\n- [ ] [Mac] **follow-up task 起票**: `feat/ws-token-enforce` (`require_token=True` default 化、Godot WS client patch 後)\n- [ ] [Mac] commit: `feat(ws): shared-token + Origin + session cap (SH-2)`\n\n## P5 — §1 hook + CI shell-bypass (SH-1、~3h)\n\n- [ ] [Mac] `.codex/hooks.json:28-39` — matcher を `apply_patch|Edit|Write|exec_command|Bash` に拡張\n- [ ] [Mac] `.codex/hooks/pre_tool_use_policy.py` — `shell_write_targets(command)` helper 追加\n  (sed/echo/tee/python-c/heredoc deny pattern)\n- [ ] [Mac] `.codex/hooks/pre_tool_use_policy.py` — shell 経路で `.steering` completeness guard 発火\n- [ ] [Mac] `.github/workflows/ci.yml` — `policy-grep-gate` job 追加\n  (banned import + ruff T201 backstop + `.steering` completeness)\n- [ ] [Mac] `tests/test_codex_hooks/__init__.py` + `test_shell_bypass_policy.py` 5 ケース\n- [ ] [Mac] `uv run pytest tests/test_codex_hooks -q` 緑確認\n- [ ] [Mac] hook smoke: `echo '{\"tool\":\"exec_command\",\"tool_input\":{\"command\":\"sed -i s/x/y/ src/erre_sandbox/x.py\"}}' | uv run python .codex/hooks/pre_tool_use_policy.py`\n  → exit 2 + deny message\n- [ ] [Mac] commit: `feat(codex): hook + CI shell-bypass guard (SH-1)`\n\n## P6 — Codex 13th independent review (~2h)\n\n- [ ] [Mac] `codex-review-prompt.md` 起草 (5 ADR + design-final.md + 検証コマンドを scope に)\n- [ ] [Mac] `cat codex-review-prompt.md | codex exec --skip-git-repo-check` 実行\n- [ ] [Mac] 出力を `codex-review.md` に **verbatim 保存** (要約しない)\n- [ ] [Mac] HIGH 全件: `design-final.md` に反映、commit/PR description にも明記\n- [ ] [Mac] MEDIUM: `decisions.md` に採否を ADR addendum 形式で記録\n- [ ] [Mac] LOW: `blockers.md` に defer 可、理由明記\n- [ ] [Mac] HIGH/MEDIUM 反映 commit (必要に応じ複数 commit)\n\n## P7 — Closure\n\n- [ ] [Mac] CI gate 全緑: `uv run ruff check src tests` / `uv run ruff format --check src tests`\n  / `uv run mypy src` / `uv run pytest -q -m \"not godot and not eval and not spike and not training and not inference\"`\n- [ ] [Mac] 重点 test: gateway / world / cli / codex_hooks 全緑\n- [ ] [Mac] `git diff --check` 緑\n- [ ] [Mac] **M9 baseline 不可侵検証**: `git diff origin/main..HEAD -- data/eval/golden src/erre_sandbox/evidence` 空であること\n- [ ] [Mac] requirement.md 受け入れ条件 9 件全 [x] 化\n- [ ] [Mac] `idea_judgement.md` (root) を移管しない (M10-0 task で別途 scaffold 時に処理)\n- [ ] [Mac] PR 作成: title = `feat(security): codex_issue.md §1-§5 統合消化 (M10 pre-hardening)`、\n  description で `codex-review.md` リンク + HIGH/MEDIUM 反映状況を明記\n\n## Risk monitor\n\n- Godot 4.4 native WS の Origin header 挙動: P4c 着手時に godot_project/ で empirical 確認\n- `_make_error` helper の location 判断: P3 着手時に gateway 内部 vs 共通 utility を判断、\n  Codex 13th review が closure 判定\n- `recv_envelope` 2-queue race-merge の CancelledError 吸収: P3 実装時に audit\n\n## Hours estimate\n\n| Phase | Owner | Hours |\n|---|---|---|\n| P0 (完了) | Claude (Mac) | 1.5 |\n| P1 §3 | Claude (Mac) | 0.5 |\n| P2 §4 | Claude (Mac) | 2 |\n| P3 §5 | Claude (Mac) | 3 |\n| P4 §2 | Claude (Mac) | 5 |\n| P5 §1 | Claude (Mac) | 3 |\n| P6 Codex 13th | Claude (Mac) | 2 |\n| P7 Closure | Claude (Mac) | 1 |\n| **Total** | | **~18h** (2-3 working days) |\n"}}
.steering/20260515-security-hardening-pre-m10-followup/codex-review.stderr:6158:/Users/johnd/.codex/sessions/2026/05/15/rollout-2026-05-15T16-24-14-019e2a85-861b-7152-9e58-45e3defa548d.jsonl:51:{"timestamp":"2026-05-15T07:25:16.091Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"function_call_output","call_id":"call_tsUruKngLLSvuA2gTHLoEC13","output":"Chunk ID: 49a267\nWall time: 0.0000 seconds\nProcess exited with code 0\nOriginal token count: 1901\nOutput:\n# Codex Review Issues\n\n作成日: 2026-05-12\n\n前回レビューで見つかった「即時修正候補」と「運用上の注意点」を、実装タスク化しやすい粒度に整理する。\n現時点でランタイム本体に即時悪用できる HIGH は見つかっていないが、Codex 運用ガードと LAN 境界には強めの改善余地がある。\n\n## 1. HIGH: Codex edit policy hook が shell 経由の編集を検査しない\n\n### 根拠\n\n- `.codex/hooks.json` の `PreToolUse` matcher は `apply_patch|Edit|Write` のみ。\n- `.codex/hooks/pre_tool_use_policy.py` は patch/direct write の target 解析だけを行う。\n- `exec_command` 経由の `sed -i` / `tee` / `python -c` / redirect 書き込みは、`.steering` 必須チェックや banned import チェックを通らない。\n\n### リスク\n\n- `src/erre_sandbox/` に `.steering` 記録なしで実装変更できる。\n- `import openai` / `from anthropic` / `import bpy` など、プロジェクト禁止事項が shell 編集で混入しうる。\n- hook が「強制機構」に見える一方で、実際には主要な編集経路を取り逃がす。\n\n### 推奨対応\n\n1. `.codex/hooks.json` の `PreToolUse` matcher に `exec_command` 相当の shell 実行ツールを含める。\n2. shell コマンド内の明白な書き込みパターンを deny する。\n   - `>`\n   - `>>`\n   - `sed -i`\n   - `perl -pi`\n   - `tee`\n   - `python -c` / `python - <<`\n   - `cat >`\n3. Stop hook または pre-commit で「実ファイル差分」を再スキャンする。\n   - `src/erre_sandbox/**/*.py` に cloud LLM / `bpy` import がないか。\n   - `src/erre_sandbox/**/*.py` に `print(` がないか。\n   - `src/erre_sandbox/` 差分があるのに recent `.steering/YYYYMMDD-*` が不完全でないか。\n4. CI に同等の grep gate を追加する。ローカル hook は補助、CI を最終防衛線にする。\n\n### 検証\n\n```bash\nuv run ruff check src tests\nuv run mypy src\ngit diff -- src/erre_sandbox .codex/hooks .codex/hooks.json\n```\n\n## 2. MEDIUM: WebSocket gateway が既定で `0.0.0.0` + 認証なし\n\n### 根拠\n\n- `src/erre_sandbox/__main__.py` と `src/erre_sandbox/bootstrap.py` の既定 host は `0.0.0.0`。\n- `src/erre_sandbox/integration/gateway.py` は `/ws/observe` を認証なしで `accept()` する。\n- `docs/functional-design.md` と `docs/architecture.md` には「LAN 内前提、認証なし」と明記されている。\n\n### リスク\n\n- 共有 Wi-Fi や誤公開環境では、agent state / reasoning trace / dialog envelope が LAN 内の任意クライアントに見える。\n- 不正クライアントが多数接続して session / queue / handshake 資源を消費できる。\n\n### 推奨対応\n\n1. 既定 host を `127.0.0.1` に変更する。\n2. LAN 公開が必要な場合だけ `--host 0.0.0.0 --unsafe-lan` のような明示フラグを要求する。\n3. MVP でも軽量な shared token を入れる。\n   - HTTP header: `X-Erre-Token`\n   - query parameter はログに残りやすいので避ける。\n4. `Origin` チェックまたは許可 client subnet の設定を追加する。\n5. `Registry` に最大 active session 数を設け、超過時は handshake 前後で close する。\n\n### 検証\n\n```bash\nuv run pytest tests/test_integration/test_gateway.py tests/test_integration/test_multi_agent_stream.py -q\n```\n\n## 3. MEDIUM: repo-local Codex 設定が network access を広く許可している\n\n### 根拠\n\n- `.codex/config.toml` に `web_search = \"live\"`。\n- `.codex/config.toml` の `[sandbox_workspace_write]` に `network_access = true`。\n- プロジェクト方針は「クラウド送信なし」「ローカル推論で完結」。\n\n### リスク\n\n- prompt injection や誤操作により、repo 内容・評価データ・研究メモが外部へ送信される余地が増える。\n- 「クラウド LLM API を必須依存にしない」制約と、Codex 作業環境のネットワーク許可が混同されやすい。\n\n### 推奨対応\n\n1. 既定は network off にする。\n2. web search は必要時のみ明示許可にする。\n3. `.codex/config.toml` にコメントで、network を有効化してよい条件を書く。\n4. 外部送信を伴うコマンドやブラウズ前に、ユーザー承認を必須にする運用を AGENTS.md に追記する。\n\n### 検証\n\n```bash\ngit diff -- .codex/config.toml AGENTS.md\n```\n\n## 4. MEDIUM/LOW: eval CLI の `--memory-db` が既存ファイルを無条件削除する\n\n### 根拠\n\n- `src/erre_sandbox/cli/eval_run_golden.py` は `--memory-db` に任意 `Path` を受ける。\n- natural capture で `memory_db_path.exists()` の場合に `memory_db_path.unlink()` する。\n\n### リスク\n\n- ローカル CLI 前提なので攻撃面は小さい。\n- ただし誤指定で任意ファイルを消せる。特に絶対パスや重要な sqlite ファイルを指定した場合に危険。\n\n### 推奨対応\n\n1. 既存 `--memory-db` を削除するには `--overwrite-memory-db` を必須にする。\n2. 既定では run 専用の一意 temp path を作る。\n3. 許可ディレクトリを `var/eval/` や `/tmp/erre-sandbox/` に制限する。\n4. symlink を拒否する。\n5. tests に「既存ファイルは flag なしで消えない」ケースを追加する。\n\n### 検証\n\n```bash\nuv run pytest tests/test_cli/test_eval_run_golden.py -q\n```\n\n## 5. LOW: WorldRuntime の envelope queue が unbounded\n\n### 根拠\n\n- `src/erre_sandbox/world/tick.py` の `_envelopes` は `asyncio.Queue()` で `maxsize` なし。\n- gateway 側 per-client queue は bounded だが、runtime と broadcaster の間は無制限。\n\n### リスク\n\n- broadcaster 停止・遅延・例外時に runtime 側 queue が伸び続ける。\n- 長時間実行時のメモリ増加が見えにくい。\n\n### 推奨対応\n\n1. runtime queue に `maxsize` を設定する。\n2. heartbeat / agent_update は最新値 coalesce を検討する。\n3. dialog / error / reasoning trace は欠落させない方針なら別 queue に分ける。\n4. overflow 時の warning envelope または metrics counter を追加する。\n\n### 検証\n\n```bash\nuv run pytest tests/test_world tests/test_integration/test_gateway.py -q\n```\n\n## 6. LOW: `_audit_stimulus.json` が CRLF 化して `git diff --check` に失敗\n\n### 根拠\n\n- `data/eval/golden/_audit_stimulus.json` は内容差分ではなく改行コード差分に見える。\n- `git diff --check` が trailing whitespace として失敗する。\n\n### リスク\n\n- レビューで実質差分が読みにくい。\n- CI や pre-commit に `diff --check` を入れた場合に失敗する。\n\n### 推奨対応\n\n1. `_audit_stimulus.json` を LF に正規化する。\n2. `.gitattributes` に JSON の LF 固定を追加する。\n3. Windows 由来の評価成果物について、rsync / copy 後の改行コード確認を手順化する。\n\n### 検証\n\n```bash\ngit diff --check\n```\n\n## 確認済みチェック\n\n前回レビュー時点では以下を確認済み。\n\n```bash\nuv run ruff check src tests\nuv run ruff format --check src tests\nuv run mypy src\nuv run pytest -q\n```\n\n結果:\n\n- `ruff check`: pass\n- `ruff format --check`: pass\n- `mypy src`: pass\n- `pytest -q`: `1386 passed, 33 skipped`\n- `git diff --check`: fail (`data/eval/golden/_audit_stimulus.json` の CRLF 起因)\n\n## 推奨着手順\n\n1. Hook / CI の編集ガード強化。\n2. WebSocket gateway の localhost default + explicit LAN opt-in。\n3. `.codex/config.toml` の network default 見直し。\n4. `--memory-db` の削除保護。\n5. runtime queue bound。\n6. 評価 JSON の LF 正規化。\n"}}
.steering/20260515-security-hardening-pre-m10-followup/codex-review.stderr:6172:/Users/johnd/.codex/sessions/2026/04/28/rollout-2026-04-28T10-50-23-019dd1c7-c483-7cc3-a653-ec2b71e8cac5.jsonl:540:{"timestamp":"2026-04-28T03:08:03.093Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"function_call_output","call_id":"call_qiZArzIMGOUXtCTCC5UkQF2d","output":"Chunk ID: 62e08e\nWall time: 0.0000 seconds\nProcess exited with code 0\nOriginal token count: 10821\nOutput:\nTotal output lines: 541\n\n     1\t# Claude Code 環境構築進捗\n     2\t\n     3\t> このファイルは構築の進捗を記録する。各 setup-* コマンドが完了するたびに更新される。\n     4\t> セッションを跨いだ継続のための引き継ぎ情報として機能する。\n     5\t\n     6\t## プロジェクト概要\n     7\t\n     8\t- **名称**: ERRE-Sandbox\n     9\t- **目的**: 歴史的偉人（アリストテレス・カント・ニーチェ・利休・道元など）の認知習慣を、ローカルLLMで駆動される自律エージェント群として3D空間に再実装し、「意図的非効率性」と「身体的回帰」を設計プリミティブとして知的創発を観察する、完全OSS・予算ゼロの研究プラットフォーム\n    10\t- **技術スタック**: Python / FastAPI / Godot (3D) / Ollama + llama.cpp / sqlite-vec / SGLang\n    11\t- **チーム規模**: 個人 (1人)\n    12\t- **重視する品質特性**: 再現可能性, パフォーマンス, 保守性・拡張性, セキュリティ\n    13\t- **構築開始日**: 2026-04-17\n    14\t- **仕様書**: ERRE-Sandbox_v0.2.pdf (21ページ, 研究企画書兼技術設計書)\n    15\t\n    16\t## 構築進捗\n    17\t\n    18\t- [x] **Phase 0: Bootstrap** (このコマンド)\n    19\t  - 完了日時: 2026-04-17\n    20\t  - 備考: 環境チェック完了、git init 実施、ディレクトリ構造作成済み\n    21\t- [x] **Phase 1: /setup-docs** — 永続ドキュメント\n    22\t  - 完了日時: 2026-04-17\n    23\t  - 作成ファイル:\n    24\t    - docs/functional-design.md\n    25\t    - docs/architecture.md\n    26\t    - docs/repository-structure.md\n    27\t    - docs/development-guidelines.md\n    28\t    - docs/glossary.md\n    29\t  - 主要な決定事項:\n    30\t    - 優先ユースケース: ゲーム開発者向け自律NPC AIミドルウェア\n    31\t    - ドキュメント言語: 日本語メイン、OSS公開に必要な箇所は英語追加\n    32\t    - アーキテクチャ: 特定パターンに縛らず、必要に応じて破壊と再構築\n    33\t    - 全5ドキュメントの横断整合性レビュー完了\n    34\t- [x] **Phase 2: /setup-claude-md** — CLAUDE.md と .steering\n    35\t  - 完了日時: 2026-04-17\n    36\t  - 作成ファイル:\n    37\t    - CLAUDE.md (87 行)\n    38\t    - .steering/README.md\n    39\t    - .steering/_template/ × 5 ファイル (requirement, design, tasklist, blockers, decisions)\n    40\t  - .gitignore 更新: なし (.steering/ は git 追跡対象)\n    41\t  - Grill me: 実施済み — 全チェック項目 OK\n    42\t- [x] **Phase 3: /setup-skills** — Skill 群\n    43\t  - 完了日時: 2026-04-17\n    44\t  - 作成 Skill:\n    45\t    - python-standards (SKILL.md, patterns.md) — Python 3.11 / asyncio / Pydantic v2 / ruff 規約\n    46\t    - test-standards (SKILL.md, examples.md) — pytest-asyncio / conftest / 埋め込みプレフィックステスト\n    47\t    - git-workflow (SKILL.md, checklist.md) — Conventional Commits / Refs: / リリースタグ\n    48\t    - error-handling (SKILL.md, examples.md) — SGLang→Ollama フォールバック / 再接続 / gather\n    49\t    - architecture-rules (SKILL.md, decision-tree.md) — レイヤー依存 / GPL禁止 / API禁止\n    50\t    - implementation-workflow (SKILL.md, anti-patterns.md) — 調査→設計→実装→テスト→レビュー骨格\n    51\t    - project-status (SKILL.md) — 動的 Shell Preprocessing Skill\n    52\t  - 動的 Skill 数: 1 (project-status)\n    53\t- [x] **Phase 4: /setup-agents** — サブエージェント群\n    54\t  - 完了日時: 2026-04-18\n    55\t  - 作成エージェント:\n    56\t    - file-finder (sonnet) — ファイル検索・分類専門\n    57\t    - dependency-checker (sonnet) — 依存関係調査専門\n    58\t    - impact-analyzer (sonnet) — 変更影響範囲分析専門\n    59\t    - code-reviewer (opus) — コード品質・可読性レビュー専門\n    60\t    - test-analyzer (sonnet) — テスト失敗原因分析専門\n    61\t    - security-checker (opus) — セキュリティリスク監査専門\n    62\t    - test-runner (haiku) — テスト実行・結果要約専門\n    63\t    - build-executor (haiku) — ビルド実行・結果要約専門\n    64\t    - log-analyzer (sonnet) — ログ分析・異常パターン検出専門\n    65\t- [x] **Phase 5: /setup-commands** — ワークフローコマンド群\n    66\t  - 完了日時: 2026-04-18\n    67\t  - 作成コマンド:\n    68\t    - /start-task\n    69\t    - /add-feature\n    70\t    - /fix-bug\n    71\t    - /refactor\n    72\t    - /reimagine\n    73\t    - /review-changes\n    74\t    - /smart-compact\n    75\t    - /finish-task\n    76\t- [x] **Phase 6: /setup-hooks** — Hook 群（3 層構成: Preflight / Guard / Report）\n    77\t  - 完了日時: 2026-04-18\n    78\t  - 作成 Hook:\n    79\t    - SessionStart: .claude/hooks/session-start.sh（動的情報表示）\n    80\t    - UserPromptSubmit: Preflight 層 / preflight.sh（毎ターン .steering/ 状態・git 状態・reimagine 状態を動的表示、BLOCK せず）\n    81\t    - PreToolUse: Guard 層 / pre-edit-steering.sh + pre-edit-banned.sh（違反ブロック + パス時 `[guard] PASS` 出力）\n    82\t    - PostToolUse: Report 層 / post-fmt.sh（Edit/Write 後に ruff format、変更時のみ `[fmt] ruff format applied`）\n    83\t    - Stop: Report 層 / stop-check.sh（ruff check + mypy、問題時のみ WARN）\n    84\t  - 出力プレフィックス統一: [preflight] / [guard] / [fmt] / [stop]\n    85\t  - settings.json: 新規作成（全 hook を `\"type\": \"command\"` に統一）\n    86\t  - 外部スクリプト:\n    87\t    - .claude/hooks/session-start.sh\n    88\t    - .claude/hooks/preflight.sh\n    89\t    - .claude/hooks/pre-edit-steering.sh\n    90\t    - .claude/hooks/pre-edit-banned.sh\n    91\t    - .claude/hooks/post-fmt.sh\n    92\t    - .claude/hooks/stop-check.sh\n    93\t- [x] **Phase 7: /verify-setup** — 整合性検証\n    94\t  - 完了日時: 2026-04-18\n    95\t  - 検証結果: HEALTHY\n    96\t  - 修正が必要な項目: 3 件 (すべて LOW、運用上問題なし)\n    97\t  - レポート: .steering/_verify-report-20260418.md\n    98\t\n    99\t## 次に実行すべきコマンド\n   100\t\n   101\t`/start-task` で最初の実装タスクを開始\n   102\t\n   103\t## 各コマンド実行前のチェックリスト\n   104\t\n   105\t各 setup-* コマンドを実行する前に、以下を必ず確認してください:\n   106\t\n   107\t1. `/context` で使用率が 30% 以下か\n   108\t2. 適切なモデルに切り替えてあるか（設計系は Opus、実装系は Sonnet）\n   109\t3. 前のコマンドが完了し、`/clear` でセッションがリセットされているか\n   110\t4. このファイル (`.steering/_setup-progress.md`) を Read で読んで進捗を確認したか\n   111\t\n   112\t## 構築物の相互参照マップ\n   113\t\n   114\tこのセクションは各 setup-* コマンドが完了するたびに更新される。\n   115\t\n   116\t### Skill リスト\n   117\t- python-standards\n   118\t- test-standards\n   119\t- git-workflow\n   120\t- error-handling\n   121\t- architecture-rules\n   122\t- implementation-workflow\n   123\t- project-status (動的)\n   124\t- llm-inference (動的)\n   125\t- persona-erre\n   126\t- godot-gdscript\n   127\t- blender-pipeline\n   128\t\n   129\t### Skill → Agent 参照\n   130\t- test-standards → code-reviewer, test-analyzer\n   131\t- python-standards → code-reviewer\n   132\t- error-handling → code-reviewer, security-checker, log-analyzer\n   133\t- architecture-rules → impact-analyzer, code-reviewer, security-checker\n   134\t- git-workflow → dependency-checker\n   135\t- llm-inference → code-reviewer, log-analyzer, security-checker\n   136\t- persona-erre → code-reviewer, impact-analyzer\n   137\t- godot-gdscript → code-reviewer, impact-analyzer\n   138\t- blender-pipeline → security-checker, code-reviewer\n   139\t\n   140\t### Skill → Command 参照\n   141\t- implementation-workflow → /add-feature, /fix-bug, /refactor（共通骨格）\n   142\t- test-standards → /add-feature, /fix-bug, /refactor（Step F/tasklist 参照）\n   143\t- llm-inference → /add-feature, /fix-bug（inference/ 関連タスク時）\n   144\t- persona-erre → /add-feature（personas/ や schemas.py の ERREMode 関連タスク時）\n   145\t- godot-gdscript → /add-feature（godot_project/ 関連タスク時）\n   146\t\n   147\t### Agent → Command 参照\n   148\t- file-finder → implementation-workflow 経由で /add-feature, /fix-bug, /refactor\n   149\t- impact-analyzer → implementation-workflow 経由で /add-feature, /fix-bug, /refactor\n   150\t- code-reviewer → implementation-workflow 経由で全実装系 + /review-changes, /finish-task\n   151\t- security-checker → /add-feature (Step H), /review-changes\n   152\t- test-runner → implementation-workflow 経由で全実装系 + /refactor 交互実行 + /finish-task\n   153\t- test-analyzer → implementation-workflow 経由で /add-feature, /fix-bug\n   154\t- log-analyzer → /fix-bug (Step 2b)\n   155\t\n   156\t### Hook → Command 参照\n   157\t- SessionStart Hook → 全コマンドのセッション開始時に動作\n   158\t- UserPromptSubmit Hook (Preflight 層) → 全ターンで動作。編集を伴わないターン（調査・質問・計画）でもプロジェクト状態を可視化\n   159\t- PreToolUse Hook (Guard 層) → /add-feature, /fix-bug, /refactor の実装ステップで動作。パス時は `[guard] PASS` で可視化\n   160\t- PostToolUse Hook (Report 層) → /add-feature, /fix-bug, /refactor 等の実装系で動作、変更時のみ報告\n   161\t- Stop Hook (Report 層) → 全コマンドのターン終了時に動作、問題時のみ WARN\n   162\t\n   163\t---\n   164\t\n   165\t## Phase 8: MVP 実装フェーズ (2026-04-18〜)\n   166\t\n   167\t実装プランは `.steering/20260418-implementation-plan/MASTER-PLAN.md` を参照。\n   168\t\n   169\t- [x] **T02 setup-macbook** (MacBook, 実作業 2026-04-18)\n   170\t  - Homebrew 5.1.6 / gh 2.90.0 / jq 1.8.1 / poppler 26.04.0 / Godot 4.6.2 / uv Python 3.11.15\n   171\t  - VS Code 拡張 ruff + godot-tools 追加\n   172\t  - `~/.zprofile` に brew shellenv を追加、`code` CLI は `~/.local/bin/code` に symlink\n   173\t  - 記録: `.steering/20260418-setup-macbook/`\n   174\t  - 設計判断 3 件: Godot 4.6 採用 / code symlink を user ディレクトリ / Python 併存\n   175\t- [x] **T01 setup-g-gear** (G-GEAR, 実作業 2026-04-18)\n   176\t  - OS: Windows 11 Home (native, WSL2 不採用) — /reimagine で WSL2 初回案を破棄し素 Windows 案を採用\n   177\t  - uv 0.11.7 (pip 経由 user install) / CPython 3.11.15 (uv 管理) / Ollama 0.21.0 (winget)\n   178\t  - User PATH 追加: `%APPDATA%\\Python\\Python311\\Scripts`, `%USERPROFILE%\\.local\\bin`, Ollama は winget が自動追加\n   179\t  - User env vars: `OLLAMA_NUM_PARALLEL=4` / `OLLAMA_FLASH_ATTENTION=1` / `OLLAMA_KV_CACHE_TYPE=q8_0`\n   180\t  - GPU: RTX 5060 Ti 16GB を `nvidia-smi -L` で確認、CUDA は Ollama 同梱ランタイムで利用\n   181\t  - 検証: `uv sync` 成功、`ruff check` / `ruff format --check` / `mypy src` グリーン、`pytest` 96 passed / 16 skipped\n   182\t  - 記録: `.steering/20260418-setup-g-gear/` (requirement / design / tasklist / decisions)\n   183\t  - 設計判断 2 件: 素 Windows 採用 (D1) / OLLAMA_* を User scope (D2)\n   184\t- [x] **T03 pdf-extract-baseline** (MacBook, 2026-04-18)\n   185\t  - `docs/_pdf_derived/erre-sandbox-v0.2.txt` を生成 (939 行 / 73 KB)\n   186\t  - `.gitignore` に `docs/_pdf_derived/` 追加、派生物は Git 管理外\n   187\t  - 想定キーワード (ERRE-Sandbox / peripatos / chashitsu / 守破離) 48 件ヒット\n   188\t  - 記録: `.steering/20260418-pdf-extract-baseline/`\n   189\t- [x] **T04 pyproject-scaffold** (MacBook, 2026-04-18)\n   190\t  - `pyproject.toml` (uv_build + PEP 735 `[dependency-groups]` + ruff ALL + hybrid strict mypy + pytest-asyncio mode=auto)\n   191\t  - `.python-version` = 3.11 / `src/erre_sandbox/{schemas.py,inference,memory,cognition,world,ui,erre}` レイヤー骨格\n   192\t  - `tests/test_smoke.py` で 7 レイヤー import 検証 (2 件 pass)\n   193\t  - `LICENSE` / `LICENSE-MIT` / `NOTICE` 正式テキスト配置、`README.md` 最小版 (EN/JA)\n   194\t  - `uv sync` / `ruff check` / `ruff format --check` / `mypy src` / `pytest` の 5 コマンドすべて緑\n   195\t  - 記録: `.steering/20260418-pyproject-scaffold/` (requirement/design/design-v1/design-comparison/decisions/tasklist)\n   196\t  - /reimagine 適用: v2 + ハイブリッド調整 3 点を採用\n   197\t  - 設計判断 8 件: uv_build 採用 / PEP 735 / ruff ALL / hybrid strict mypy / line-length 88 / uv.lock コミット / LICENSE 正式配置 / schemas.py docstring-only\n   198\t- [x] **T05 schemas-freeze** ★ Contract 凍結の核 (MacBook, 2026-04-18, PR #5/#6)\n   199\t  - Pydantic v2 で `AgentState` / `Observation` / `ControlEnvelope` を凍結\n   200\t  - `ControlEnvelope` / `Observation` に discriminated union (Annotated + Field(discriminator=\"kind\")) を採用\n   201\t  - 静的 `PersonaSpec` と動的 `AgentState` を完全分離 (橋渡しは `persona_id` のみ)\n   202\t  - `MemoryEntry` に embedding を持たせず、T10 で `StoredMemory` を別定義する方針\n   203\t  - 記録: `.steering/20260418-schemas-freeze/`\n   204\t- [x] **T06 persona-kant-yaml** (MacBook, 2026-04-18, PR #7)\n   205\t  - `personas/kant.yaml` を operational orientation (trigger→behavior→mechanism→consequence) で定義\n   206\t  - epistemic 3-tier (fact / legend / speculative) 完備、`primary_corpus_refs` は lean (orphan ゼロ)\n   207\t  - `default_sampling = (temperature=0.60, top_p=0.85, repeat_penalty=1.12)` = 後続ペルソナ温度帯見取り図の基準\n   208\t  - 記録: `.steering/20260418-persona-kant-yaml/`\n   209\t- [x] **T07 control-envelope-fixtures** (MacBook, 2026-04-18, PR #8)\n   210\t  - `fixtures/control_envelope/` を top-level 配置 (Godot developer が Python 依存なしで読める)\n   211\t  - tick=42 の coherent scenario で 7 fixture (Kant が peripatos で歩行) を束ねる\n   212\t  - `peripatetic` モード sampling_overrides = (+0.3, +0.05, -0.1) を persona-erre Skill と同期\n   213\t  - Kant speech は *Kritik der praktischen Vernunft* Beschluss 冒頭の後半句を採用\n   214\t  - 記録: `.steering/20260418-control-envelope-fixtures/`\n   215\t- [x] **T08 test-schemas** ★ Contract 凍結の境界 (MacBook, 2026-04-18, PR #9)\n   216\t  - 3 層契約ガード: Layer 1 (boundary 検証) / Layer 2 (meta-invariant: `extra=\"forbid\"` + `schema_version`) / Layer 3 (JSON Schema golden drift 検知)\n   217\t  - `tests/schema_golden/` に golden を配置 (fixtures/ と意味を分離)\n   218\t  - `conftest.py` に callable factory `make_agent_state` / `make_envelope` + convenience fixture の二層構成\n   219\t  - ルックアップテーブル方式で `make_envelope` をディスパッチ (未消費 overrides は ValueError)\n   220\t  - 記録: `.steering/20260418-test-schemas/`\n   221\t- [x] **T15 godot-project-init** (MacBook, 2026-04-18, PR #10)\n   222\t  - Phase P MacBook 側ラインの scaffold (v2: Scaffolded Handoff を採用、v1 最小ブートを破棄)\n   223\t  - `godot_project/` に Godot 4.4 互換 + 4.6.2 実機、GL Compatibility renderer\n   224\t  - MainScene 階層を patterns.md §2 に完全準拠 (ZoneManager / AgentManager / WebSocketClient / UILayer)\n   225\t  - 各 dir に README.md (`.gitkeep` ではない) で GPL 分離ルール等の文脈を即時提供\n   226\t  - `tests/test_godot_project.py` で必須ファイル存在 / Python 混入ゼロ / Godot headless boot を機械検証\n   227\t  - 記録: `.steering/20260418-godot-project-init/`\n   228\t- [x] **T09 model-pull-g-gear** (G-GEAR, 実作業 2026-04-18)\n   229\t  - 推論 LLM: `qwen3:8b` (500a1f067a9f, **5.2 GB**, pull 24 分) — MASTER-PLAN §6.3 の `qwen3:8b-q5_K_M` / `qwen2.5:7b-instruct-q5_K_M` は registry 未登録のため fallback 採用 (decisions D1)\n   230\t  - 埋め込みモデル: `nomic-embed-text` (0a109f422b47, **274 MB, 768 次元**, pull 7 分) — `multilingual-e5-small` も未登録のため fallback 採用 (decisions D2)\n   231\t  - Ollama 再起動: tray 起動が失敗したため `ollama.exe serve` を env vars 明示 export + `nohup &` で直接起動 (decisions D3)\n   232\t  - 実測: ollama load 後 VRAM delta 6.2 GB (未 load 1307 MiB → load 後 7493 MiB、総使用 ~46%)、`qwen3:8b` 日本語挨拶 `こんにちは` で応答確認 (cold start 35s, keep-alive 5 min)\n   233\t  - 記録: `.steering/20260418-model-pull-g-gear/` (requirement / design / tasklist / decisions D1-D4 + 実測補足)\n   234\t  - 関連 T10 影響: embedding 768 次元と `nomic-embed-text-v1.5` のプレフィックス規約が T10 design の `DEFAULT_DIM` / D5 に反映済み\n   235\t  - 設計判断 4 件: D1 (LLM fallback) / D2 (embedding fallback) / D3 (tray 迂回して ollama serve 直接) / D4 (2 段階 commit 戦略)\n   236\t- [ ] T10-T14 は G-GEAR 側 Phase P (MASTER-PLAN.md §4.2 参照)\n   237\t- [x] **T16 godot-ws-client** (MacBook, 2026-04-18, PR #12)\n   238\t  - 3 スクリプト完全分離: `WebSocketClient.gd` (auto-reconnect + MAX_FRAME_BYTES)\n   239\t    / `EnvelopeRouter.gd` (7 専用 signal emit) /\n   240\t    `AgentManager.gd` (`has_signal` duck typing でログスタブ)\n   241\t  - Fixture 境界分離: `scripts/dev/FixturePlayer.gd` + `scenes/dev/FixtureHarness.tscn`\n   242\t    で production path に dev コード不混入\n   243\t  - Contract ガード新設: `tests/test_envelope_kind_sync.py` で schemas.py §7 ↔\n   244\t    EnvelopeRouter.gd の kind 集合一致を CI で自動検出\n   245\t  - Godot headless 回帰: `tests/test_godot_ws_client.py` で 7 kind 順序再生を検証\n   246\t  - `tests/_godot_helpers.py` に `resolve_godot` 抽出 (test_godot_project.py と共有)\n   247\t  - MainScene.tscn: 3 script attach + EnvelopeRouter ノード追加 + signal 配線\n   248\t    (`load_steps=6`, 手動編集 — 次セッションでエディタ canonical 化予定 L5)\n   249\t  - 設計フロー: v1 素直案 → `/reimagine` で v2 再生成 → 比較 → v2 フル採用\n   250\t    (V1-W1/W2/W4/W5/W6 を構造で解消、design-comparison.md に比較表)\n   251\t  - code-reviewer HIGH 1 + MEDIUM 3、security-checker HIGH 1 + MEDIUM 1 対応\n   252\t  - 全テスト 100 pass / 15 skip、ruff / format / mypy 全緑\n   253\t  - 記録: `.steering/20260418-godot-ws-client/`\n   254\t    (requirement / design / design-v1 / design-comparison / decisions / blockers / tasklist)\n   255\t- [x] **T10 memory-store** (G-GEAR, 設計 PR #15 + 実装 PR #16, 2026-04-18〜19)\n   256\t  - 設計: `.steering/20260418-memory-store/` (requirement / design / tasklist / decisions D1-D5)\n   257\t  - /reimagine 適用: v1 (単一テーブル + embedding BLOB + strength カラム) を破棄、**v2 (kind 別テーブル + 共有 `vec0` + 関数 decay)** を採用 (D1)\n   258\t  - 設計判断 5 件: kind 別テーブル + 共有 vec0 (D1) / decay ハイパラ λ=0.1, β=0.2 (D2) / Procedural / Relational は最小 DDL (D3) / 設計ロック分離 (D4) / 埋め込みプレフィックス強制 (D5)\n   259\t  - **実装 (PR #16)**:\n   260\t    - `src/erre_sandbox/memory/store.py` — 4 kind テーブル (episodic / semantic / procedural / relational) + 共有 `vec_embeddings` vec0 virtual table (embed_dim=768)、async API は `asyncio.to_thread` で sqlite3 wrap (`check_same_thread=False`)、`knn_ids` / `evict_episodic_before` / `list_world_scope` 補助 API 公開\n   261\t    - `src/erre_sandbox/memory/embedding.py` — `QUERY_PREFIX` / `DOC_PREFIX` 定数 + `embed_query` / `embed_document` / 低レベル `embed` の 3 段 API (D5 強制)、httpx.AsyncClient、失敗を `EmbeddingUnavailableError` に正規化\n   262\t    - `src/erre_sandbox/memory/retrieval.py` — 純粋関数 `score(importance, age, recall, cos)` + `Retriever` クラス、per-agent…821 tokens truncated…it__.py` — 7 シンボル top-level re-export\n   301\t    (`OllamaChatClient`, `ChatMessage`, `ChatResponse`,\n   302\t    `OllamaUnavailableError`, `ResolvedSampling`, `compose_sampling`,\n   303\t    `DEFAULT_CHAT_MODEL`)\n   304\t  - `tests/test_inference/` 新規 (23 件): sampling 8 件 (境界値上下完備) /\n   305\t    adapter 15 件 (MockTransport + `test_close_is_idempotent` +\n   306\t    `test_injected_client_not_closed_by_adapter`)\n   307\t  - 設計フロー: v1 素直案 (error-handling examples.md 直移植、10 弱点) →\n   308\t    `/reimagine` で v2 再生成 → v2 フル採用 (V1-W1/W2/W4/W5/W6/W7/W8/W9 を\n   309\t    構造で解消)\n   310\t  - 設計判断 8 件: D1 Contract-First 採用 / D2 `/api/chat` / D3 frozen\n   311\t    ChatResponse / D4 sampling 分離 / D5 sampling 後勝ち / D6 エラー正規化 /\n   312\t    D7 `qwen3:8b` default / D8 7 シンボル re-export\n   313\t  - code-reviewer HIGH 2 + MEDIUM 5 + LOW 4、security-checker MEDIUM 2 + LOW 4\n   314\t    を総合評価 → 即対応 6 件 + 保留 5 件 (blockers.md BL-1〜BL-5)\n   315\t  - 全テスト 157 passed / 23 skipped (134 baseline から +23)、ruff / format /\n   316\t    mypy 全緑\n   317\t  - 記録: `.steering/20260419-inference-ollama-adapter/`\n   318\t    (requirement / design / design-v1 / design-comparison / decisions /\n   319\t    blockers / tasklist)\n   320\t- [x] **T12 cognition-cycle-minimal** (G-GEAR, 2026-04-19, feature branch)\n   321\t  - MVP M2 の核となる 1 tick 認知パイプライン (1 エージェント分の CoALA + ERRE\n   322\t    9 ステップ)\n   323\t  - `src/erre_sandbox/cognition/state.py` — CSDG 半数式 (MASTER-PLAN B.3 MVP 優先 #2)\n   324\t    の pure function: `advance_physical(Physical, events) -> Physical`\n   325\t    (4 要素導出 sleep_quality / physical_energy / mood_baseline / cognitive_load) +\n   326\t    `apply_llm_delta(Cognitive, LLMPlan) -> Cognitive`\n   327\t    (valence/arousal/motivation/stress)、`StateUpdateConfig` dataclass で係数調整可、\n   328\t    `Random` 注入で決定論化\n   329\t  - `src/erre_sandbox/cognition/parse.py` — `LLMPlan(frozen BaseModel, 8 フィールド)`\n   330\t    + `parse_llm_plan(text)` JSON 抽出 (code fence 許容、brace balancer で引用内\n   331\t    ブレース処理) + `MAX_RAW_PLAN_BYTES=64KB` DoS ガード (security M1 対応)\n   332\t  - `src/erre_sandbox/cognition/prompting.py` — 3-stage system prompt\n   333\t    (`_COMMON_PREFIX` → persona 固有 → 動的 tail、RadixAttention 最適化) +\n   334\t    `build_user_prompt` (最新観察 + memories + JSON スキーマヒント)\n   335\t  - `src/erre_sandbox/cognition/importance.py` — event_type lookup +\n   336\t    intensity/emotional_impact/importance_hint 補正 → `[0, 1]` clamp\n   337\t  - `src/erre_sandbox/cognition/cycle.py` — `CognitionCycle.step()` 9-step\n   338\t    orchestrator + `CycleResult(frozen BaseModel, llm_fell_back flag)` +\n   339\t    `CognitionError`。LLM/Embed 不通と parse 失敗の 3 経路を単一 fallback に\n   340\t    畳み込み、それ以外は crash-loud (error-handling Skill §ルール 5)\n   341\t  - `cognition/__init__.py` — 13 シンボル top-level re-export\n   342\t  - `tests/test_cognition/` 新規 46 件: importance 7 / parse 11 / state 10 /\n   343\t    prompting 8 / cycle 10 (happy path + ollama-fail + parse-fail +\n   344\t    embedding-fail + reflection trigger + sampling override + speech/move 分岐)\n   345\t  - `pyproject.toml` — `tests/**` per-file-ignores に `S311` 追加 (テスト seed\n   346\t    用途での Random 許容)\n   347\t  - 設計フロー: v1 素直案 (1 関数、regex p